Dream: I was an antelope in a stony landscape with brush. I was not hunting in it. I only saw it and it ran away when I saw it.

I dreamt that theives came and were slaughtering a man. Then a few chaga men were attacking a Hadzabe man named Musa.  I started to scream "stop killing him, stop killing him," but the man was already dead.

I dreamt a buffalo hit me. I was in Numbeya bushland where we look for honey. I was looking for the "small honey." There was another man called January and he came and helped me. I tried to run to climb the mountain to escape.
I dreamt I fell into a well that is near the Hukumako area by the Dtoga people.  I was with two others and one of my friends helped me get out of the well.  I know the mean who were with me.
I remember being chased by an elephant in a location around camp. I escaped.
I dreamt I was being chased by a lion and I climbed a tree near the Endagoga mountains. I was alone. When I climbed the tree the lion just waited for me, then I woke up.
I went to dig alone and when I was digging I was attacked by a lion. I was at the Hukomako mountains near camp. The lion caught me and I woke up at that moment.
I dreamt I was chased by an elephant in the Mwasadi mountains all the way to the Dubukela mountains; I survived because I climbed on top of the second mountain.
I dreamt I was taken by an elephant but I do not recall the place.  I was chased by an elephant, but I escaped as I woke up.

I dreamt I was being chased by hyenas. I was hunting, I shot an arrow at the leopard and it ran away and I continued to hunt. The area I was in was unfamiliar and I was alone. I got meat from an antelope the leopard was eating.
I was fighting with a baboon in the Garagu mountains. I was alone. I was hunting and I killed a small baboon and that's when I was attacked by a large baboon and I ran away to escape.

I was cut in the stomach by a guy I didn't recognize.  I shot an arrow back to the attacker and before it hit him it turned into a rope that tightened and wrapped around his body; it bound the attacker.  We, my two friends and myself, wanted to go after him but the man yelled "I will kill you if you come after me!" It was in Gidamilanda.
I was chased by an elephant in the bush around camp.  I was with four unfamliar women.  I escaped by running into the mountains.
I was chased by an elephant. I was in Endaboga. I was alone. I escaped by climing the mountains.
I dreamt of witchcraft here in Sengele; there were no familiar people or animals.  The witches were digging up a body to get it to perform a spell.
I was chased by a hyena.  It was at the place I go to collect water.  I escaped the hyena.

I dreamt I was going to join the military.  I was in a place in central Tanzania (Mwanioni) and my friend and myself were getting interviewed for the military.  Fifty people were needed for the military but I was the 51st interviewed; when I was asked if I wanted to go I said 'yes' and went into a black car.  I physically forced myself into the car.

I was with my friend Dofu and we were workin together and Dofu got paid 90,000 shillings and gave me 30,000 shillings because he said our camp was starving.  The work was practicing shooting arrows. There were many people there. When I came to camp a child threw shit at me and I woke up. I didn't recognize the kid.

I was hunting birds on the mountains with others.  I hit the bird and ran after it but I fell into a rift which was a crack in the ground, and braced myself in the crack to keep from falling into it. I yelled to my friends but no one came. The place was unfamiliar.  Once I got out of the crack in the earth, I continued to hunt.

I had a dream I was fighitng with my friend; we were in Mongola.  We were moving from our current camp to Mongola; there were many kids and women as well; I recognized many people I saw a really tall guy from another camp that I recognized.  We began a long physical fight without weapons.  We endup up both going into a truck with so many people I had to ride on the top of the truck.  I was hit by a branch and woke up.

I was chased by an elephant; I was lost and I ran into the Kwisanakwebe mountains; after escaping the elephant I tried to find my way home and instead found a lion eating an antelope; I saw the lion and climbed the tree but then the lion climbed and transformed into a very dark black man who I did not recognize.  The black man climbed down to use the camp but reached a riverbed and couldn't pass; then I saw my grandparents, but they wanted to fight me; while I crossed the river (which was up to my chest) my grandfather hit me in the mouth with a stick and it cut my lip. They tried to drown me and I punched my grandmother in the face and woke up.
Giraff. In the bush, close to home. I was hunting the giraff. I killed it. I skinned the animal. I carried it to camp. Then I woke up and there was no meat. I saw five other men I knew.
I was chased by a leopard in nearby mountains.  I began by hunting but realized that I was the hunted. I was alone but I escaped. The place of the dream was the nearby mountains.
I had an argument with the Domanga camp because they got money from the Hadzabe fund but we didn't.  I even faught with my older brother.
I was chased by an elephant. I was in endaboga. I was hunting and that's when an elephant caught me unpreppared, but I escaped by climbing the mountain.
I dreamt a Toga not from this camp took a knife and a person he didn't know from another camp.  After I told the guy to stop he left our Sengele camp.

Two of them hunting a zebra. I told my brother to shoot the animal. The animal wasn't dead after his brother shot it. It got away. He woke up wondering if he had a zebra, then realized it was just a dream. I was in camp, at home.

I dreamt I was fighting a leopard.  I went to collect honey; I found  a honey guide that took me to a boabob tree; when I got close to the tree I heard a leopard growl; I took my arrow to chase it off; as I waived the arrow and the axe I yelled louldy and scared it.  When it ran away I continued looking for honey but it came back and I threw a rock scaring it again for good. I was at Kumwaka; when I screamed my brother came and helped me scare away the leopard.
I went to search for noney in Engalow and I heard a group of baboons.  I went after them and killed one of the baboons with my arrow and the rest ran away.
I was hunting. Someone was shooting an animal. And that's when a kid killed the little dear this morning. It tooks place around the camp area, and the kids was someone from camp, but unfamiliar.
I had a dream that Kaunda and myself found an atelope in Endagoba and we shot it.  We then went back to camp to get help from all the men to track and butcher the kill.
I almost got bit by a snake. I was walking int thh bush and suddenly the snake appeared and raised its head. I was black.  It was around here near Sengele and the snake was poisonous.

I dreamt a lion was eating a zebra. I tried to get the meat but then the lion turned and was trying to kill me. I do not remember the place and I was alone.  I survived by running, but I was very afraid.

I was dreaming I was around the area, and a guy I recognized bit him. The dream was around sengele, in the area. A man bit me; there was an argument and I was fighting and I couldn't beat him up and the guy bit me.

I dreamt I was in Yaeda at my maize farm; when I went to the farm I found some cows destroying my crops.  I went to the execuative warden officer to show the damage. There were other young people from my home waiting for me. When I walked to the warden I woke up.
My son was killing a baboon here at the camp.

I was with Ngele, a honey badger; I was attacked by him and it pushed me down and after a fight I threw it away.  I recall the setting, it was nearby the camp. I was looking for small honey when the attack happened. I was almost killed.
I dreamt I was being chased by a heard of elephants; I was in Nyanza, which is open flat savanna land. I ran and found a small cave which was too small for the elephants to follow.  I escaped.
I dreamt I was chasing a feral dog and ran it into a cave.  I was trying to get it for meat.  It was very near camp.
I was bit by a scorpion in camp while gathering firewood and it struck me on my finger.  I woke up, looked at my finger, not knowing if it was real or not.

I dreamt I went out to collect honey by the river near camp and when I was close to the honey I saw a lioness and her two cubs.  I was only a very close distance from the lion and she jumped at me to attack. I dodged and threw my axe all while pulling out my bow and shooting an arrow at the same time.
I dreamt of the woman who just died. I cried so much I thought I would die. It was here in the camp.

I was being chased by a leopard in the Byshana mountains.  I was with four people. We were all women going to dig for tubers and the leopard came. I got seperated from my group during the chase and then woke up.
I was chased by a Toga man in the Mkelenge mountains. It was just me and the Toga man chasing me. I ran and escaped because the man couldn't catch me.
I was chased by a Hyena in the Engarao mountain area; there were four other people I knew, all female.  We went to work for digging and when we came back to the camp the hyena attacked by we ran.
I went to dig with a  group of five women from camp.  We were digging when the elephant appeared and we scattered.

I dreamt I was being chased by buffalos in the mountains of Endabojo; I was with three women (Anina, Agenise, Melimo) and all of us climbed on the tree to escape.  I was running and the branches of the tree hit me in the eyes and that's why my eyes hurt right now.

I dreamt I was fighting with someone from Mongola; I was fighting with (adult male) and I beat him up very badly. It started when I was walking and when he threw a punch all of a sudden.  My friends (Bokhe, adult male/adult male) my dream seperated me from him.

I was on top of an unfamiliar building.  I slipped and fell; I was with Benjamon and I needed his help to keep from falling all the way down and so he reached out to touch me, but did not pull me up. I fell down and died.
I dreamt I was fighting with my brother at Gidamilanda; I was making an arrow and the brother came and said "this is my arrow!" We faught and my two friends seperated us but then I woke up.

I dreamt about a snake. I was in Sengele and I was in my father's house, Mzee Onawasi.  Inside, there was a tree that was part of the house and within the branches was a snake that my father found after looking at the tree. When the snake came out my father caught it with his hands.
Last night dreamt his mother was coming home from Thanry. He dreamt she was on the trail. No animals. It was a good dream.
Dreamt he was with many people dancing and then his house flooded full full full of water. It was a river.
Dreamt she gave birth to twin girls.
Dreamt she gave birth to a girl outside her home. In her dream, she was alone and was holding onto a post to push. It was a good dream
Dreamt a Bantu man was beating her and she ran away. It was a bad dream.
Dreamt her husband found a second wife (woman unknown). Her daughters refused to accept the second wife. It was a bad dream.
Dreamt she was bailing water and getting many fish and killing many fish. It was a good dream.
Dreamt she was bail-fishing, and was bailing water and getting many fish and killing many fish. It was a good dream.
Dreamt he was in the forest and the military was chasing him with guns and he climbed a tree to get away. He was in a forest he knew, but he did not know the soldiers. It was a bad dream.
Dreamt she was walking in the forest with her two adult daughters and found a porcupine in a trap and brought it back to the village to eat it. It was a good dream
Dreamt she was in the forest alone and chased a procupine and killed it with a machete on her own and brought it back to share with the camp. It was a good dream.
Dreamt bosolo and moshimo (her son and niece) were on the path from thanry. A good dream.
Dreamt the military shined a flashlight in his face and he woke up. It was a bad dream.
Dreamt his other wife was alone on the trail coming back from Thanry. It was a good dream.
Dreamt he was alone and caught a mosome in a trap. It was in a forest place he knew.
Dreamt he went to the forest past his house (place known) to check his traps, and a porcupine was in his trap. He went to check his traps alone. He brought porcupine back to share with his family.
Dreamt he was at the river alone and all the animals in the forest were chasing him and he ran away as quickly as possible. It was a bad dream.
Dreamt he went fishing with hooks alone. It was a good dream.
Dreamt he went to the river with fish hooks and left them at the market
Dreamt of animals. He dreamt he went hunting with a gun in the forest.
Dreamt SLL bought a big pig (njua) and gave some to her to cook and then mendi shared a plate with SLL. It was a good dream.
Dreamt a Bantu man (known) gave her meat and she came back and shared it with her family. It was a good dream.
Dreamt she was out alone with her husband near Ndongo camp. They were cutting trees to look for honey. It was a good dream.
Dreamt she was putting boma in the water.
Dreamt he was planting plantains alone in his garden.
Dreamt of bread. He was eatin bread. Lots and lots of bread alone. It was a good dream.
Dreamt of the big animals--elephants. Went hunting with spears with many animals. Didn't kill an elephant. It was a good dream.
Dreamt he was climbing one of his palm trees to collect palm nuts (alone)
Dreamt she woke up and saw a dead person. Many people came to see the dead person. It was a bad dream.
Dreamt the Jengi (dangerous forest spirit) was chasing her and she was running away and then the Jengi stabbed her and her family in the chest. It was a bad dream.
Dreamt sister and bro-in-law were on their way home from the forest. It was a good dream.
Dreamt baby X was nursing with mother (daughter of her half sister). Woke up crying. A very sad dream.
Dreamt the military was hitting people in the village all over the place. It was a bad dream.
Dreamt he went fishing at the kombi (fence fishing) alone. He found many fish. It was a good dream
Dreamt his body had many many wounds for three days and then it passed. It was a bad dream
Dreamt she earth was giving birth to bananas straight from the ground
Net hunted many animals in the forest. It was a good dream.
Dreamt he was net hunting with his family (including extended family camp) and that they caught many many animals so he had to make a smoker "bota" to smoke all of them. It was a good dream.
Dreamt was out at a forest camp hunting and her family caught many porcupine. Forest known. It was a good dream.
Dreamt MO (farmer male, some of village elder, boat driver, and occasional field assistant) came on the boat with new arrives. Everyone was waiting for the boat on the river together

Had two dreams. In the first, he dreamt he was dancing with a forest spirit "mokondi" and the spirit talked to him and shared knowledge with him. In the second, he dreamt he saw an elephany while he was in the forest alone, at a spot he did not recognize. The first was a good dream. Did not provide valience for the second.
Dreamt people came to the camp with their spears. It was a good dream.
Many animals ere chasing him and he climbed a tree and the animals passed and he came down. It was a good dream.
Dreamt many animals were chasing him and he climbed a tree and then the animals passed and he came down. It was a good dream.
Dreamt he was walking in the forest alone and found a turtle and picked it up. A good dream
Dreamt SLL gave her money and she went to buy palm wine "lotoko" which she gave to me and then her mother and her sat on a matt with her. It was a good dream.
Dreamt her mother gave her money and she went to buy molenge and drank and was happy. It was a good dream.
Dreamt she was in her house and then was washing in water alone. It was a good dream.
Dreamt she was in the forest hunting with her husband and they got many animals and then she collected mela (tuber). It was a good dream.
Dreamt they got many animals and collected mela with her husband. A good dream.
Dreamt he was alone in a boat going to get palm wine on the river. He did not recognize the palm tree. It was a good dream.
Dreamt she went vail fishing with the two female researchers (MSS and SLL). A good dream.
Dreamt she went to the forest and got food from the garden. She worked the garden alone. It was a good dream.
Evening with friends. I see Charles Leclerc (F1 driver) playing on a simulator. I will soon come back a friend, also a big fan of F1

In a hotel, on one side everyone is queuing to go to the bathroom (large room with several baths). All kinds of eccentric people. I come back from a jog. I go to my room, I take a moment to find the locker that corresponds to my room. A childhood friend is there, storing food in a cooler. We quickly go to the swimming pool. There are arm wrestling tournaments. Drawing lots I only find myself facing a guy 2x more muscular than me.

In a zoo, I find myself stuck in the enclosure of the elephant, very docile we become "friends" (like with a dog) I come back later, he is much older. Besides that, I'm trying to get a little girl to do homework. She works on the future but does not succeed and refuses to do them
In the street, a man annoys, insults a young black woman who is with her handicapped daughter in a stroller. I don't get mad at him.
Great meeting between friends, buffets where everyone cooks. For me -> cucumber toast, cream. When suddenly. a tsunami
On a motorcycle with a friend, I became unable to drive with someone behind me.

Went on vacation with friends, we took 2 cars. Our car gets lost, so we stop in a small restaurant/village. We sympathize with people. I have to force a friend to leave because she never stops talking. We put all the things in the car, the driver leaves without us. we finally meet at the airport. Slippery road even if it's not raining. We fell because the bike was leaning too much and not enough speed. I'm angry, frustrated to not have aniver there, and very sorry for my friend.
Nightmare: bacteria possessing human body. bacteria in lip, unable to control body. Bacteria kill before tearing two
A friend introduced me to these new sports sneakers with marbles in the sole.
motorcycle ride, I find myself on small gravel paths. Very fun to drive there.
I was looking for something

I was in the paddling pool with my friend's son who is 20 months old. I never with him in the water, we had fun. He had a shovel and a red bucket. At one point, I was teaching him to swim. In reality, I accompanied my friend and her son to the paddling pool at the end of July, but I did not swim there. In the dream, I called him by his first name "Ilyas", I see him regularly so he knows me well. In the dream, he came easily towards me, followed me. I was talking to him and he understood what I was telling him
Dream of my Chinese colleague surprised because she was pregnant adventures and walks in the woods
Because of the dream due to an airplane, I get up very quickly. I just remember dreaming of a woman

I dreamed that I was a former gangster. I see another gangster. We educate young people to follow another path. At one point I take my comrade to leave. He declares in public that he regrets his life before. But I know that's wrong. He ends up admitting to me that he regrets nothing at all and that he is proud of his previous life. I am furious and hit him, he remains on the ground without moving.

I had met the researcher of this study at the station with other participants. A girl was there to say that she can't go on because she found a job in a study at UniGe. At the end me and another girl started to sing a song

I remember being a dream with a particular point of view, it seemed to me that I was an observer according to my point of view. Everything was strange. A guy asks god for help. God gives him a car , but he had to return it later. But he didn't. So God came back, driving a white car, and punished him for not having to return the car to fulfill his promise.
The environment was very etange. It looked like he was claustrophobic even though he was in an open space.

I remember the dream with my dog. I had to take someone else's dogs to a place where my family members were. Dogs weren't leashed to get there, my little dog was walking around and my aunt's big dog bit him on the back. I was very angry with my aunt, because she didn't care, besides, she was never a good person for me. She spoke to me, but I did not answer her. A second part of the dream, I was in a place that looked like a small amusement park. I met people, including one from Portugal. We had to leave this place to go elsewhere. As we walked the Portuguese hugged me and we walked like that for a long time.

I remember checking my boyfriend's backpack. I found a kind of pendant with a key and a small leather satchel. I open this satchel and I find condoms. I immediately asked my boyfriend. I was a little angry. He was there, didn't say anything, he laughed, because I'm jealous
I was at the Balexert shopping center. I was rollerblading inside the mall and a security guard was chasing me.

A friend tried to steal a pair of shoes from a well-known store in Geneva. I was like a secret observer to help the security guards catch him. I had to remain discreet so that my friend would not notice my presence. It was a dream from an outside perspective

I was on a SBB train. I didn't pay for the ticket, so I was a little nervous to be picked up by a controller. I had stayed in a city that looked like Barcelona, ??but suddenly I was in a forest with coconut trees. I tried extracting coconut water from it to give to people around me. Suddenly, it looked like the mall and shoe store from the first dreams were around the forest.

Me and someone who looked like my brother were in a city and got involved in a family. They had 3 big mansions where they took people in gruesome sacrifices. As soon as we arrived at one of the mansions, we quickly found out what they had done and tried to evade them. He had one of their employees chasing us all the time. It was a long race trying to escape them. we were considered a great potential danger if we went to the authorities and told them what was going on inside their properties. We finally left town with a stolen car, but they were still chasing us for the rest of our lives because we were the only ones who escaped.

The dream wasn't very clear, but I remember being with my family and a couple of family friends. In the dream the couple had come to visit the town where we grew up. The couple became very rich and came to our city in a luxury car. I was very jealous and sad that I didn't have the opportunity to have a successful career like them.
I had a different cell phone than the one I usually have.

I was in the benches of the audience at the University of Lausanne, and there were also other people in my family (my parents and my sister). There was going to be a concert, but the singer arrived late and people ('the audience') started to leave. When the singer arrived, there were only a few people left (including me and my family). But the singer seems a bit lost and didn't know the lyrics, nor what he had to say, (the singer was an old gentleman, ~70 years old)
I dreamed that I woke up too late, around 3 p.m. and that I had missed the virtual reality session which was scheduled for 9 a.m.

I dreamed that I was making a transfer with my father, but it did not work because the name of the recipient was not the correct one.
Indeed on the payment slip, there was not the name of my father but rather that of my ex

I dreamed that I was going down a fairly dark stairwell (I did not recognize the place). On each floor there was an automatic jet of disinfectant spray that cleaned the shoes before you could go to the next floor.

I went to visit my best friend Glyole, 32, [she lives in Los Angeles], we were in my house which looked like the one I lived in San Francisco. We were on his bed and I showed him a baby, we were playing with the baby.

I was in an elevator, stuck, alone. I pressed the button to go down, and then the elevator went down at full speed. I was very scared, I tried to ring the emergency bell
I arrived at the bottom, it was dark and a sheet or blanket fell from the ceiling of the elevator to cover me.

I was at uni [resembled UniGe] with friends from unige [I had sent him a message that day] - Sab at 24, I had a problem with my card so went to see the reception. they helped me and we left. We walk in the city but it looked like Montreal [where I did my Bachelor] I saw lots of streets that I knew, I was moved because I missed this city and I had/I have very beautiful memories [I had discussed Montreal + McGill with a friend of mine from my time there that day too] We entered a house with a lot of girls like the ones I knew at McGill but not exactly those people either the. I was shy, I tried to organize my classes while they were chatting and doing lots of other things. I suddenly see that one of the girls is a girl I recognized, it was Isabel [a childhood friend that I haven't seen for 20 years ++] It was strange, she must have ~30 years. The room has changed to accommodate other activities with other people that I did not know.

I was with my girlfriend -31 years old- in a building with a place that sold or prepared food or drink for Mike, (30 years old) a boy we know, he had a bowl of tomatoes on the counter. We passed in front of it and we decided to take it, to steal it. He saw my girlfriend doing it and she said we were hungry. Later, I was there again and a security guard was with Mike and he was explaining the situation to him. The agent also had a bottle of mine and I got the feeling he was trying to match the 2 things but Mike knew we were the ones who took the tomatoes.

In the first dream, I was in an apartment that I didn't recognize there were friends my age but I don't know who, it was a party I think, my girlfriend (she is 31) was there too , she was sitting next to someone else towards a balcony, or next to a window. I looked at her and I saw that she was smoking cigarettes, she had one in each hand and I got angry, I left the room, she came to find me and I got angry with her [ 3 years ago I pushed her to stop smoking, she did, but lately she smokes when she drinks or when we go out and there are other people smoking: it makes me angry at each time, it was so hard for her to stop the first time]

In another dream I was with a friend named Phil who is 31 years old [we haven't spoken in a long time, I called him a month ago to check in] also had his girlfriend, we were getting ready to go camping, with our bikes and our things in backpacks. Phil had a very nice and electric bike and special bags to store his things that folded. We were in a place a bit like Burning Man, in a desert.
I lived in a small house with my two (invented) grandmothers and we hosted friends, I was a top athlete and I was secretly in love with my coach. As the dream progressed, I got dirtier and dirtier.

In one of my dreams, I thought I woke up in my bed. I then had to fill in the sleep diary. However, I knew that I had to start filling it from 09.09, but I did not know if it was the night of 8.09 to 9.09 or the night of 9.09 to 10.09 [this is something that made me think yesterday evening, I did not want to distort the study]. I remember sitting on my bed with my back against my cousin. I took a pen, but when filling out the diary, I realized that I had just spent the night from 6.09 to 7.09. I then told myself that I was stupid and I put the diary back on my bedside table [this is where I leave the sleep diary and the dream book]. I lay down on my bed being a little nervous because I always plan in advance what I'm going to do and there, it didn't go as planned.
I also dreamed that my watch was scratched and in my dream I thought it was a dream. I then woke up and immediately fell asleep.

In this dream, I was on a huge flat roof. I was with people I didn't know. We were two teams, each on one side of the roof. The other team had a raised wall at the top of their roof, while my team had a passageway with a door down into the building. I felt like we were a lot compared to the other team who were supposed to be 2-3. In fact, it was a video game (Call Of Duty WarZone) in reality. There were plenty of weapons and equipment on the ground. The person on my left found a good weapon, but I only found miniature weapons as if they were made for dolls. In the opposite team, there was a person on the left on the wall and a person on the right on the wall with a snifer (we could see the bezel shining with the sun). Since I had no weapon, I went through the passage with the door. In this dream, it was daylight, bright sunshine. But there was no sound.

This dream was clear when I "lived" it, but I only remember small bits. * It was my birthday and there were my friends [I couldn't see their clothes] and other friends but family. I think there were cakes, but I don't remember what. * At one point my mother was angry and said of a small child that he or she [can't remember] was badly brought up. * At one point, someone had just climbed into our attic (I was afraid in this part of the dream because the person was dangerous) into our attic. My mother and I were in my room (the attic and above). I remember telling him to whisper because he could hear us. [It seems to me that the person in the attic was dangerous]. In this dream everything happened in my house, nothing changed me compared to reality, apart from the hatch to go to the attic which was in my room instead of being in the hallway.

In this dream, we were first sitting outside with the guests. Suddenly, our living room has turned into a sort of concert hall with a stage that can go up and down. I wanted to sing but my (my mother's reaction made me sad and angry) mother yelled at me something. [I don't remember what it is, but it's true that even if I want to, I don't sing in front of others because I'm afraid someone will say something to me]. He was a little boy who started to sing [he sang well]. Everyone was happy. In the living room, at that time, the lights were blue, a bit like in concert halls. The boy was brown.

In this dream we are in an amphitheater at uni. It seems to me. There are students and their parents (only mothers). I'm at the very top [I usually put myself at the bottom] and my mother is lower on the right. I don't know the teacher at all [he has no face in my dream]. It's actually a lesson on insects. I don't remember the course at all. At the end the teacher asked us which insect could build something between two wooden posts. I proposed the hornet [although I have never participated in a course]. But the teacher replied that it was the spider that can indeed weave webs. In this dream I don't know anyone except my mother and the mother of a student. Everyone was talking, there was a lot of noise. I was a little interesting [I was like that in primary, but something has changed since]

This dream, it seems to me, follows on from the second, but I didn't see any parents there and there were a lot fewer students. This time, I had many friends of mine. This dream was actually a kind of race. You had to be the first team to finish showering. The showers were like cabins in swimming pools. I remember we were talking but I don't remember what. The atmosphere was rather friendly, joyful.

In this last dream, I was with friends with whom I play football. We wanted to train on a field that is not that of our club [I have never seen it]. I'm on my bike in the rue de Lyon, I go up it quietly until I reach the place where my mother's old office was. In front of the latter is Charlotte waiting for me kindly. Finally, the child explains to me that his father works at the hospital and that his name is Owen. I bring the little one back to the hospital with his father, who is none other than Owen from Grey's Anatomy. Once my BA for the day is done, I go back to the practice, but I obviously completely missed the time for my anatomy oral exam. I just see a gray tabby cat catching a mouse. As he catches it, a giant mousetrap appears out of nowhere and slams the cat. (I don't know where it was).

I was lying in my bed with my blankets on me, I also had my headphones (my earphones for music) on my head. The song playing was light my fire. I could hear it very well and I could concentrate individually on each element of the song (drums, singer...) and I took off my headphones, but the music continued and I heard it perfectly (I found very strange). I took off my headphones just as the piano solo started, I could hear the song very clearly and I could perfectly detail my room.

I was in a car (a minivan) full of people I don't know, I was sitting in the back, but I had a good view of what was going on in front. And then (it was night on the highway which was lit) a motorcyclist slipped by on his back on the road as if he had just fallen off his motorbike. Then, we always stayed on the left lane on the road because on the right lane, there were always broken down cars with people on the lane who had put a triangle so that we could run into them. And then I notice that the person in front of me is a woman holding a microphone out the window. And every time we passed by a broken down car, the car and the people next to it would fly as if a huge gust of wind had carried them away. (The sequel takes place during the day but it remains the same dream). Then we see the curly woman talking into a microphone and looking at a camera and holding in her hand the big microphone she had held out the window and she said in front of the camera it happens to everyone to make foolery. (What I understood was that it was an RTBF car and the woman was recording broken down cars with her mic, but the mic was making everything fly around her). (Ah yes, and the farm reported no injuries).
I could clearly see a guard following down a long, lavish hallway that was sure to be in the Vatican.

It was a strange dream that I happened to experience several times. I am in my street, identical to reality. On my right, there is a field belonging to my dad (he is a farmer). It climbs steeply and above there is a small path that leads into the woods. We can see fir trees and I know that there is a wolf chasing me. It's far away and I have plenty of time to return to the house, located at the start of the street, a little over 100 meters away. However, I can no longer move forward I am frozen. I know he's getting closer but I'm glued to the ground. I feel it very close, I cry. The scene repeats itself, he's far away, getting closer, but there's no way to move forward. However, I never saw the moment he grabbed me, only the chase scene. Then I wake up, quite disturbed, even if I still slept well.

I go to war against these bosses who supervise women by giving them orders. I woke up hearing myself pronounce this sentence. I was in a bright room, conference room type, very bright. I was at the front, as if I were the instigator of a general revolt. Unknown people listened to me obediently but did not follow the movement I was trying to start. I was pissed off by their inertia.

I dreamed of a place not very well defined. It looked like 2 rooms like a dining room and a living room. In the other room was my dad, Manu's, one of my former teachers, and I think we had finished eating. We played with small plaster figurines, they were locomotives but painted like cows in black and white. Then Manu's father groans because Manu and I had more than him. Manu explains to him that it's because I had taken mine from home, but he doesn't believe us and leaves. It makes me laugh too much... And I look at Manu and tell him that he will never change. Then we take our train cow and roll it into the other room, on all fours. Suddenly we leave, Manu remembers that we must not forget the box of cabbage.

I had just gone to a restaurant with friends and on the way back we went to a café for a drink. The decor is dark, everything is bronze and gold (glasses, cups, etc.). When paying, my code does not work. I start trying all the combinations to no avail. And then the waiter says it's nothing and offers us a drink for the trouble. We sit on high stools with strings on which raw pasta is tied and we eat it as we go.

I find myself in a room that reminds me of nothing but tearing small sachets (almost the same as the mini sachets of salt found at Quick or MacDo). In these bags, there are very small spades of different colors without relief with the effigy of the characters of the Harry Potter saga. I'm very happy because I collect them.

Then I remember being in front of a computer screen. Long lists of formulas scroll before my eyes. I am anxious, as if I had to hurry to avoid being caught in the act. Afterwards I find myself on a chair, like a prisoner although I am not tied up. I think I'm a secret agent. The image is clear, a tall man with gray hair is several meters from me. We are in a room with orange colors. I laugh honestly because he can't do anything against me, even if he seems to have caught me.

I find myself in the department store in my city, it's very late and I'm with two people who are my friends (but they don't look like my real friends at all). In fact, we can eat whatever we want, so we are each in a department and we nibble a chocolate candy from each package. It's awesome. Then suddenly we're in the parking lot of the store (but it's more like my high school playground) and we're shopping carts with rollerblades on our feet.

I'm in a small room with three people who only stare in disgust. There is a woman in her 40s with brown hair permed in a rather BCBG gray suit. I don't know her at all. They tell me that I lied, that I never had my diploma and that the score I did in the elections is therefore not admissible. I never lied, I have my diploma. Yet I remain motionless without saying anything. They add that I will not find a job. Then afterwards, I see myself walking down a street lined with very white houses. I'm in a small room with three people who don't look on with a look of disgust. There is a woman in her 40s with brown hair permed in a rather BCBG gray suit. I don't know her at all. They tell me that I lied, that I never had my diploma and that the score I did in the elections is therefore not admissible. I never lied, I have my diploma. Yet I remain motionless without saying anything. They add that I will not find a job. Then after, I see myself walking in a street lined with very flowery white houses, with a lawn in front of each (the kind of American street that we find in Desperate Housewives). I am happy. I eat pasta at a small stand by the side of the road, got there I don't know how. flowery, with a lawn in front of each (the kind of American street that we find in Desperate Housewives). I am happy. I eat pasta at a small stand by the side of the road, got there I don't know how.
my brother asks me to drive a truck in a narrow street (I think it was my girlfriend's street).
I just remember that I'm a warrior and I have to save someone (a girl I believe).

I walk in the street and I see my ex whom I try to deny but who challenges me (I no longer remember the conversation that followed and the street in which I was walking looked like a street in Liège). Then I continue on my way and I hear beeps that sound like those of a bomb. I grab this one which turned out to be a bomb and I scream to take cover because there is a bomb then I try to throw this one as far as possible and I run to get to the shelter and when the bomb exploded I felt burning pains then I put myself on a child to protect him from the blast of the explosion. After when I got up the scenery vaguely resembled my old school. After having recognized the sets, I leaned on a banister and I saw my brother who was playing belotte with the boyfriend of my sister-in-law's sister and 2 strangers then I had feelings of discomfort following the burns and someone asked me if I was in pain then they asked me if I wanted to play belotte to replace one of the two strangers when I wanted to play I couldn't spread my cards in my hand. Then I saw my mom asking two of my high school friends if they would like to do a karate demonstration and they complied (while doing Bruce Lee screams) then one of my two friends said it's cinema.
we go up to an attic (that of my house) and once in the attic the scenery changed and I no longer recognized it. Then we had a barbecue with sauerkraut and merguez
I don't remember the exact dream but when I woke up I was quite panicked, breathing fast and I had ??? so he was pretty scary.

There was a kind of party at my house (but the places were unknown to me) and at the beginning there is no one except a little girl of 4-5 years old with whom I befriend and who follows me everywhere holding my hand. Then people known and unknown arrive. I go into the garden in which there is a large glass staircase.

I was at home (the house was totally foreign to me) I surprised thieves, a young girl and a kid. I talked to them, they were very nice. I drank coffee with the girl while the kid stole my jewelry and I didn't say anything, I thought it was normal. This dream was very bright.
I was babysitting with two boys aged 5 and 6. I got mad at them because they were insufferable didn't do their homework and didn't want to eat their pasta.

I dreamed that I was visiting patients at home. I was going to a friend's house and endlessly ringing the doorbell without success. This frustrated me because I was wasting a lot of time. His house was located in a huge office where the employees told me that my friend had left. This dream was quite innocuous apart from the fact that almost everything was blue (the walls, ceilings, ambient light, clothes...)
I had to work on a piano sonata to play it. I didn't know where to start, it was complicated. I had to be able to play it on a 3/4 grand piano.

With several people, I don't remember exactly who, we were walking towards a very particular café. He had a peculiar appearance. A central aisle ran through it, it was lined with a few tables where several people I knew were seated. Among them were my parents and history teachers from my secondary school. The table where my parents sat was almost unique because there was no table around it. Other tables to my left were four people and often there was no more room. I cared about a place where people were.
I dreamed that I had a draft.
Car race that ends in an accident.

I dreamed that my mother was pregnant with a girl. We tried to find names, my sister and I, but nothing suited my mother. The day of the birth has arrived. We were waiting for the contractions to be strong to call an ambulance, then the little girl came into the world, we were all happy but I was afraid and I was sad that my mother took care of the baby more than me It was happening at home in the Congo.

I dreamed that in Belgium people were drawing lots from among the population to replace the king and it happened to me. People kept talking about me on TV, I was very happy at first but afterwards I was too afraid of not knowing how to run the country and so I wanted to give up my place.

My dream happened in Congo and Belgium at the same time. I was with my mother and one of her friends. We were looking for his missing son. He was suspected of taking drugs and was found in a ravine with his bicycle. He wasn't moving I was sure he was dead His mother was crying, took him in her arms and then pulled him out of the ravine in a black blanket. We met at my house, in my kitchen (in the Congo) and we put him on the floor, and he got up. I was afraid it was a ghost but it was him. He had ended up in the ravine because he had been knocked out.
I dreamed that I dropped my actimeter in the water and it stopped working You were very upset and sent me home
We were going with my wolves to the 100 years of the ???. The dream takes place in ???, I have 50 children to hold and I lose more and more, they disappear, evaporate.
My dream takes place in Brol, I walk my wolf cubs, they are wise, they sing but I manage to adjust their voices.
I woke up with blood in my mouth, and I cried in my sleep (wet cheeks)

Dinner for 6 people, 3 men in their fifties and my father, my brother and me. We ate dried mushrooms a bit like crisps. And my father had taken way too many on his plate for everyone to have, so in the end everyone was served except me because there was no more to eat.

Show where I was going with baptized medicine but when we arrived on the scene I realized that it was rather a small performance made by children. The people I was with disappeared and I settled on the floor. The organizer once called the children to come and start the show and to stand on the side of the stage, it was not a raised stage, people were sitting on the ground in a semicircle and the show took place in the semi-circle. All the children were there, except one who was near me because she was too scared. The lights went out, I gave the little girl a flower necklace as the show started and then led her to the edge of the stage with the other children.

I dreamed that you decided not to take me in your study anymore. And that you hadn't notified me by cell phone. So I find myself at the cyclotron in front of the door without anyone coming to open the door and I have to take the bus to the chemistry stop where there is a whole gang of boys with a cap each on their head. They started teasing me and then I don't know how I ended up in a car with a girlfriend. We were surrounded by the boys and they were trying to turn the car around.

I dreamed that the other volunteers of the experiment came to annoy me in my room, preventing me from sleeping, which in my dream caused the experiment to fail Nathalie arrived and sent them back to their room.
I dreamed of a vacation, I was abroad with friends of mine, who had their names but did not look the same. This trip had a purpose that I was trying to direct but I can't remember which one.

I was with a friend, she wanted to go to the hairdresser to fix her haircut a bit and I took the opportunity to do it too, but it was not my usual hairdresser and he spent the whole day trying to fix my hair but he couldn't. My mother arrived and it was a general crisis
a friend of mine got pregnant

I was in Greece where I spent a week this summer and we were on the beach when a wave covered everyone except my brother, my sister, the lifeguard and me. Those that the wave carried away turned into seals. We 4 had to find a key which was in the hotel room and which opened a wooden box.

The dream takes place in the countryside with my grandparents (where I haven't been for several years). The house is identical to reality, except that a delivery man comes to drop off lots of computer equipment and electrical appliances and the house is transformed into a stronghold, with surveillance cameras and motion detection, etc... And in the garden there are sort of big holes like in a cemetery before you put the coffin in it. And my grandfather explains to me that times are no longer safe and that a prowler is prowling around and killing people every night in the village. Night falls and everyone present is anxious and angry. And I see a kind of passing shadow outside and I know it's the killer (who looks more like a kind of werewolf than a killer for that matter...) But I don't tell nobody because I don't want them worrying for nothing. There I see my parents looking at me strangely as if they knew we wouldn't see each other again. The next image I'm in the middle of a meadow, still at night and I'm running because I'm being chased --> suddenly awakened by the cat.

It takes place in my elementary school, the places are identical to those in the past, except that the people are their current age. It's break time, all the people are gathered outside and we're grouped into small groups because there's been a murder in the playground and we have to solve the case. The corpse is covered with a sheet and there is blood all over the walls of the school. The atmosphere is tense and everyone gets angry because rumors say that the assassin is still on school grounds. Then this crime story disappears and we start playing volleyball. Then the bell rings, all the classes gather in rows in the same places as in the past. But in the row, an old childhood friend hits me, we start fighting on the floor, I realize it's my cousin but we keep fighting and at one point he turns into my current cat, but with blood all over the place, he limps away, jumps the low wall that surrounds the school, jumps into a passing car (a big car converted into a house that I'm sure I've seen in another dream that night). The car pulls away and the cat stares at me sadly. And I start crying because I know I won't see him again and I feel guilty for hitting him. (And during the whole last part there was a song that stuck in my head all morning but I couldn't put a title on it.)

We were leaving for a school trip to the high mountains. After a walk in the middle of the cliffs we arrived at the refuge where we were to sleep at night. We arrived late because we were laughing among ourselves and we took the wrong path. The refuge was a huge wooden house leaning against a mountain. We had to choose our beds from the bedrooms, but on one of the remaining beds, there was a huge dog that was drooling and had taken over the territory. So we laughed among ourselves to find out who would take this bed and we teased Adrien so that it was him. Having fun in this dream, I was happy to go on a trip with my friends.

Same characters but this time we had class. Except that the course took place in the street at the foot of a monument that vaguely resembled a church. Each of the students (around 6 in all) was at a wooden table and the teacher (a very cute teacher by the way, but I don't know him) was explaining the day's lesson to us. We had to decipher the mystery of dreams to access sacred science and finally understand when we are dreaming or not. And the lesson was interrupted when tourists passed in the street (therefore in the middle of the tables) and asked us for directions.

There was a big sun in my dream and I was in my countryside sunbathing and I decided to do summary sheets of my small animal lessons. Once finished, I found it so surprising to have worked of my own free will that I decided to put an announcement on the Internet portal of the university to offer to photocopy my summaries for those who did not go to class. But the one who answered me is a person from the amphitheater that I don't particularly like so I was wondering if it was morally honest not to give him my summaries or if I was obliged now that I had passed the 'announcement.

Initially, I had to infiltrate a wooden hut which turned out to be very large inside. We had bows and we came across a friend from football, so I didn't dare do anything to him. Then it's confusing, the scenery often changes incoherently… I find myself in the streets of Liège and nothing concrete is happening, I find myself a little in circles by bus and in the streets. Then I realize that I'm being chased by a kind of robot that needs my heart and one of my lungs to develop. It happens and he becomes giant, but I never see him, I just hear his footsteps and his voice. I find myself at home with my little brother and we have to fight but without knowing anything to do, hence the feeling of frustration. Then my brother's idea, the old gas can on the roof of the school that I'm climbing so and there example of physical pain, in the wrists because I stand on the roof with one hand and the can of the other. Then the can is empty I fill it with what is left in the mower. Put it outside and throw a match in it hearing the footsteps, I wake up...
football match where I do absolutely everything I want without any problem

I wake up in my room and a colony of little 5-6 year old boys come in all excited. We were going on a trip with football. I get up and we are immediately at the station looking for our platform (very strange platform not with several platforms and several tracks but one track (drawing). Part of the group has already boarded the train at a place on the platform and we run to get to the end of the platform before the train.Once inside it looked more like an airbus...I woke up.

Then I played on the banks of the Meuse with my brother at football but not enough space so we went home (minimum 80km). On the way my brother is replaced by one of my cousins ​​who was advancing on a snowboard (without snow and even on the climbs) when she is completely unsportsmanlike. She makes me try it and the snowboard went off without me, I couldn't catch it and jump on it. He ended up on the other side of a highway, I crossed with no problem. I bring the snowboard back to my cousin who replaced it (my cousin) and wake up. During my dreams, sudden character changes do not bother me at all.
I was with an ex-girlfriend and we just got together like we hadn't seen each other in a few weeks. We were at her house but the house did not correspond at all with reality.

I dreamed that my boyfriend gave me a gold watch, which was really not beautiful and I couldn't take it off. I didn't dare tell her that I didn't like her and I was disappointed with her gift. My mother arrived and told me that no one from my family could come and that they had forgotten my birthday anyway. I was super sad, I kept crying and no one saw or heard me. I was saying things but it was as if I didn't exist. It was the kind of dream where you are in a place where you cannot go out and where there is no scenery. Finally, there everything was orange with a kind of haze.

Initially, we were celebrating Easter at my house, everyone was looking for gifts outside, except my niece and me. Lots of eggs fell on the ground, they were everywhere. Then we went to a big building that looked like my secondary school but with the doors of the Forum de Liège. It was still Easter because they were throwing eggs from the balconies but everyone was dressed up. My niece was still with me and I spoke with my ex-stepfather who I haven't seen for a long time. There was some kind of restaurant where my mother was sitting with people I don't know and my boss's sister from the Forum. They all ate lasagna except her, who was expecting a 55-minute rib steak and caused a scandal. The waitress had forgotten her and she had to wait another 1/2 hour. On the menu, behind the waitress, there were plenty of pizzas.

I am in my bathroom and I feel a presence. I ask whoever is there to come forward thinking of something supernatural. My towel then begins to hover in the air, I understand that it is a spirit. I feel like I'm having a conversation with him. My mother arrives, I ask her to come see something fun. I don't know if the towel starts again in front of her.

Miss Christina was talking to me. She told me that the night of habituation (for the study) showed that I did not correspond to the criteria to pass the study. So I was paid 14 euros for that night. Hehehe
I didn't hear my alarm clock go off, and I missed the exam. It was horrible and I woke up in a hurry.

I find myself in the courtyard of the Blanc Gravier residence. I am in a wheelchair and alone. The sky is gray and there is no sound. I wonder where I'm going to go to meet the lady at the reception of the building. There is no access ramp at the entrance. I'm already trying to turn around with my chair in an awkward way. I almost fall forward. I have a jump of fear. I try to climb a small step but have no strength in my arms and the wheels fall back to the ground. I try again once or twice. I can't do it and I'm still alone in this empty courtyard. The weather is grey. I am completely pissed off and feel helpless and frustrated. It's not possible that there is no suitable passage, I tell myself. Just as upset, I find myself in the skin of Hélène Quittu (me) yesterday. I saw again the face of the student who doesn't want to change rooms next year (she's settled in the only adapted room at Blanc Gravier). I also see the lady at the reception with her annoyed and helpless look (as if to say, I don't know how to do anything). I see again the objects-furniture of the room and especially of the unsuitable bathroom. I realize that it is no longer up to accessibility standards anyway (the building was built 20 years ago). I imagine the disabled student already not knowing how to go to the toilet because there are no handles around the potty. The bathroom is old. The lady at the reception tells me that her managers, building managers, do not want to do anything and want to leave this room to current non-disabled students. I am revolted, irritated, nothing is adapted the only adapted room is occupied by students who do not want to move and no one seems to want to change things. I imagine contacting my manager who has more influence than me to change things but already thinks that it will take forever for me to get an appointment to explain the situation to her and thinks that this problem is not not his priority. I will still try to contact her, I tell myself. My dream ends there, I remain frustrated and angry. I wake up for a moment thinking to myself, it's not true.
Diner (fries) in the kitchen very faithful to reality with the father, the mother and my ex-girlfriend. We were talking but I don't know what, then suddenly we found ourselves in the car.

We were (with my friends from Rheto) at the bottom of my garden sitting or lying in the grass then we went to the garden next door which in my dream was a field and there were 2 ponies including a whole whole little. He lay on his back for me to caress his stomach. The other was a little bigger, especially very big. I asked if I could ride it, I was told yes, so I rode it and it immediately galloped off, I was happy. I quickly went down because we were all going around a table in a courtyard at the back of a house (I don't know which one). We sat down and Mireille arrived with a kind of little bucket filled with fruit (fruit salad) and there was someone else with a bucket too but I don't know what was in it anymore. said it was a good idea. Then we remained seated and I remember that we were waiting for other people. They arrived and we enlarged the circle around the table to be able to add chairs.

I was at the end of a class, the people who came out had just attended a kind of seminar on the environment I believe because a young boy (about 14 years old) who remained from the meeting came to talk to me. I don't remember exactly what he said to me, but I totally agreed with him. He said that he agreed with what had been said at this meeting on the protection of the environment etc.... I replied that it was good that young people like him were interested in that etc. ...

It happens more or less in the same place, I'm in a class with other people. At first there is no teacher so I keep busy and do something else. My boyfriend tells me not to stay there because a teacher is coming and I won't be able to get up (he's in the back of the room, there's a lot of fights) Indeed, a teacher enters the room . He is rather old and he is super friendly. He kindly asks that we put away our things to listen to him. Since he's very nice, I can't do the opposite but it bothers me because he's starting a lesson on a subject that I know very well and my boyfriend tells me, you see, you should have left earlier. He stays in the back of the class and at one point there is a mouse that escapes (I don't know from where). My boyfriend managed to catch up with her.

I'm in my bed, in my room. I wake up and I see my trainer arriving. We start talking a bit and he tells me that I won't be playing the next game. I tell him it's normal since I'm slightly injured. He tells me that's not why it's because I was playing badly at the moment. In short, I get a little nervous while getting dressed and when I left, I woke up.
The clarity of the dream is quite dim but I remember we were all in a park, on the grass and in the sun, just having a good time together.
Very briefly, I just remember someone shampooing me.

The dream starts with a dog (doberman) that I can't hold. We're both in a white room and the dog is jumping up and I can't think of anything else to do but grab onto his neck with every jump and find myself being propelled into the air with him every time. time. Then after a while, I find myself at my grandmother's, in her kitchen, introducing her to the Doberman as my new dog, but I have trouble holding it. My mother is there too and it seems that we stopped at Grandmother's on the way while we were going to Saint-Malo to take the new doggie for a walk. On this Grandma announces that she too has new dogs. A very fat mastiff, a tall, slender greyhound and his real dog, a black Labrador, arrive. Then we meet in front of the entrance to Grandma's house in her garden with her me and Mom to say goodbye. But no one wants to leave. We may tell each other that we will see each other again soon, but no one can. As I tell her that I don't really want to leave her alone, she tells me that she is not left alone. She takes me back into the kitchen and there is a tiny blond boy, whom she introduces to me as Jojo, a cousin of Hugo who is 17 months old and who is going to stay with her for a while.
I remember a mini-football field.
I don't know why, but I was organizing an escape and someone was chasing me. I was trying to go home but the places did not correspond to reality…
I was having a drink in the evening at a terrace and there was a kind of small demonstration. I see friends that I will join and say hello.

We had a discussion between roommates. One wanted a dishwasher, the other not but the arguments of one and the other did not convince the other. Me, I was for the fact that it consumes less water than washing up by hand and also because it's boring to do the dishes and against, because it's too expensive. There you go, the three of us were debating.

My roommate being absent every Sunday, it's me who takes out the trash on Sunday evening and there I dreamed that Cécile came home around midnight and came to see me while I was sleeping to ask me if I had taken her out.

I find myself in a room at Home, where everyone usually meets to discuss and exchange the times of the day. I am alone, sitting with my friend Moussa (Malian 22 years old) around the common table. I discuss with him something that does not come back to me and gradually we start laughing.
Very confused dream (impression) I only remember that each character was in the shoes of another.
Last night I dreamed that I found myself facing her in the same place she had called me to during the day, except that she was facing me. We covered the topics discussed on the call.
I find myself in a forest trying to catch a turkey (poultry). They tell me that I have to be careful otherwise she's going to catch me because she's smart. It happens in broad daylight.

The dream was a bit like a slideshow of blurry photos with a buzz in the background. The photos looked like a lot of landscapes or scenes of daily life but in countries other than Belgium, such as Arabia, Egypt, India, countries of the former USSR...

This dream traced a new form of time management and my life to optimize my performance. There were no specific places, nor characters, just the places related to sport, swimming pool, track, wood for mountain biking and some weight machines related to the physical preparation of which I dreamed. The ideas were very clear, the image less
The Manga was Akira. I mainly reviewed the striking or poorly understood scenes during the viewing…

I remember I was with another person but I don't know who. We were chased by killers but I don't know who and for what reasons. We took refuge with an old lady, in an old farm full of hunting trophies. Then I remember that hunters came to the old lady for a day of hunting and in these characters there was a friend of mine. And this buddy in question actually goes hunting with me. I remember a specific image but not a continuous story.

I dreamed that I was studying veterinary medicine but the premises did not correspond at all to the premises of my faculty. We had to do dances and each group had an armband. The one in my group was yellow. When the time was right, two men arrived, one of whom was a former vet and a member of the clergy, but the other I don't know. However, I don't know why but I arrived late with friends. In a panic, I put on my yellow and pisete armband. I stood next to my group. But they had a red armband and the others in yellow called me. I didn't know them and I didn't know the piece he was doing. So between two dances I was swapped. At the end of the dances, the ex-veterinarian collapsed all of a sudden. We were appalled because we thought he was dead. They gathered us in a big room. The person who had fallen lying on a table in front of us. The other person, a man I didn't know, proceeded to tell us that the person lying in front of him was a high ranking man in the church, that he was still part of our community despite having entered holy orders. and that he was not dead. He took out several vials and mixed them. Then he gave it to the inanimate person saying we should move away. Bubbles came out of his mouth and he went into spasms. Then I started running around the room because I had something precious, I don't know what was going to serve me next. A fat guy I didn't know was chasing me.

I dreamed that we were in class with my class. Finally, more exactly, we were in TD with an assistant. It was going well until someone started asking lots of questions. She realized that another assistant had misled us about the composition of an organ. She got angry and left leaving us 1 hour of beating but watched. We were talking and a boy I don't know came up to me. We left the TD room for an adjacent room. He asked me if I wanted to go out with him but it was no I found him repulsive. He didn't want to let me go anymore and I started crying with anger and frustration. I was angry with my boyfriend for not being there to get rid of it. Someone has come to put an end to this. I went back to my place and someone tried to get me???
I just know that I put a snake around my neck.

With Célia, my roommate, we were visiting a house in Tiff for next year. We liked her a lot and we decided to take her. We were settling in and friends from lecture halls came to see us because they wanted to buy the house. And finally with Célia, we didn't take the house because there was only one bedroom.

I was having sex with Nico, my boyfriend, outside in a field. We were surprised by 2 girlfriends of mine. We had a quilt and hid under it. It amused us. Then afterwards we discussed and I told the story of a girl from our amphitheater who had a baby during the year and who has therefore stopped her studies for the moment. I felt moved and cried.
My pathology professor was retiring and we had organized a farewell party for him. It happened in the amphitheater.

My dad was working on a scaffolding that looked more like a thrill ride. It was at high altitude. The scaffolding was wooden. At one point, there was a risk of an avalanche. We were afraid for the people who were working. I was with other people but I don't remember who.
I was having sex on the washing machine in my house in Tiff. And then my brother entered the room.

I find myself in my mother's school with one of her colleagues who is currently retired, Martine. We had a class of students. At one point a little girl hurt her leg, she actually broke her leg. And I was being asked to do something.

My landlord went to the house (in Tilff) to see the state of the house (because the house has humidity problems and he has to ventilate). There, he comes to see the mold. But he decides to do nothing. So I insist that he do the ventilation for us because with Célia we are tired of always cleaning everything with bleach and always having fog on the windows. But there Célia does not insist and acts as if she didn't care.

I came home from classes with Célia. We live right next to the university, so we were on foot. Then we notice that Céline is running after us. She's a girl that I don't like at all who, moreover, doesn't like anyone except Célia and who always needs Célia to make decisions. There she comes to tell Celia (because she doesn't talk to me) that she doesn't want to go home that she doesn't want to be alone that she wants to stay with Celia. Me, drunk, I leave and go home. Then a few minutes later, they both arrive at the house. And Céline insists on doing genetics (work on the course) but only with Célia and suddenly they lock themselves in Célia's room.

I was in a stable and there were problems with insect infections. The owners (whom I don't know) had tried a pesticide but it didn't work and asked me to do something. The pesticide they used was a yellow box. I notice that the insects had become resistant to the product. I make them try another product.

Location, river with waterfalls it's confusing. At first I am with Nolwenn and Julia and I argue with Nolwenn for colored pencils. Then I find myself in front of a first waterfall and I jump to reach the other bank using a vine. Finally, I find myself in front of a second waterfall and there are my sister Laurence, my brother-in-law Eric and my nieces. They teach me to jump this waterfall also with a vine. We start over several times, it's like a game. So for a moment I read a message on my cell phone, my mother wished me a happy birthday. Otherwise I remember that I was wearing a t-shirt throughout the dream.

I'm at my sister's in France and I have to go back to Liège because I have a lab in the afternoon. So I'm trying to contact Maud (it's the one I carpool with but to go to Besançon). Then, I try to contact her to find out where the meeting point is, but I can't find her contact details because my mobile phone has run out of battery. With my mother, my sister and my brother-in-law, we meet in a kind of café-restaurant and there I ask for a directory to try to find the contact details, but I can't find them. We look at the time and it's too late to arrive on time at the TP then finally I realize that I can take the train.

I also dream where I find myself in a restaurant with lots of friends from my class and we eat around a big table I think I was celebrating my birthday. Another dream, I find myself at a physics lab with my class. And Nolwenn (my friend) tells me that I've talked about her to others. I tell him it's wrong, I feel sad and lost.
I find myself at a physics lab with my class. And Nolwenn (my friend) tells me that I have talked about her to others. I tell him it's wrong, I feel sad and lost.

I am in the hospital where I am doing many examinations. Then I find myself at my grandmother's (but it's not her house) and she teaches me how to cook and finally we meet at the table with my grandfather and my uncle. During the meal, I eat meat.
I'm at my sister's house. There are people at home (family, friends). Virginie tells me that I am in good health.
It's very fuzzy and very vague. I just remember that I was in a kind of darkened cafe with Erasmus students. We were in Tromso in Norway and we saw the snow falling through the window.
I was plugging in my phone in an apartment that I don't know with my father then my watch starts ringing my mother comes to see us then the dream stops.

It looked like an action chase movie in which I was the hero. I only remember a few sequences but I know that it was consistent throughout and that the events and my decisions were logical and consistent. Chase in a night train, I was trying to recover a very important object/document from the hands of criminals (terrorists?). Very spectacular unarmed and firearm combat, I have teammates but I don't remember them distinctly except for one, I had a kind of flashback to his childhood where he lived in a gigantic landfill and fed on the remains of badly emptied cat boxes. I still have the taste in my mouth. A moving little speech with my daughter (lol, I don't have a daughter myself) where I tell her that I'm doing something dangerous but I have to go because it's important. The bad guys are in some sort of dizzying building (but no dizziness, feeling of being invincible/invulnerable). I climb it with my bare hands then very acrobatic fight suspended/hooked to the building which looks like a rocket launch pad then alarm clock.
A red-ocher brick hallway of a school building. There is a plaque fixed 2 meters high on which it is written, warning, in rase of blurring, current can be dangerous. The corridor is really very high.

I dreamed that I was still in college in a class of retarded morons. Later, frustrated, I ruminate in a public park near a tree (cercis siliquastrum) and I meet an old widow who lives just in front of the park. We discuss and there I discover that she is the widow of a crazy composer who composed a work that I play (in the dream) on the violin, the manuscript of the black bible (an enigmatic thing). We become good friends and when she dies she bequeaths me her husband's watch which would contain the secret of her work but bam, I wake up and it's over.

I dreamed that I forgot to take off the actiwatch for swimming lesson. The pool was much bigger than I remembered and there were gigantic diving boards. The path to get there was labyrinthine over several floors.
I dreamed that I received an extremely detailed email from the person from whom I am currently buying a bow by mail order.
I was in Thailand with my girlfriend.

I was on a TV show, as a contestant. My whole family was in the audience. The other participants were misses, very pretty. The object of the game was to solve puzzles hidden under boxes that each participant possesses. I no longer know how one of my competitors was setting traps for me. In the end, we left the TV set to discuss it. It all ended in a general fight. I no longer remember the details.
We had to return an important file to EPFL. We were too late, it was stressful.

We were outside, presumably on top of a mountain. A teacher was there. She explains to us that we had to carry out an important architectural project, to place poles under the Rolex learning center in order to prevent it from collapsing in the future. We made sketches on the floor. Anecdotally, at one point, I overheard a classmate's discussion about a boy. A very critical discussion. I thought she was talking about me, but it wasn't.
Canada wanted to buy an African country with a few billion dollars. This was controversial around the world, some detractors argued that it was the beginning of a new phase of slavery.

I was in a station, vaguely resembling the Renens station that I frequent. I bought my ticket. Strangely, I used both a 200 Frs note and my credit card to pay. Then something struck me. I remember I was stressed. So I left my 200 Frs and my C.B. on the ATM for 1 minute, while I went to check something. On my return, of course, the card and the ticket had disappeared. A group of girls were sitting on sofas 4-5m from the ATM. As I was convinced that one of them was the thief, I told her give me back my 200 balls and my C.B. What she did. Only I later discovered that a second credit card was missing. I just missed the train. I found myself alone.
I created people by mixing a spirit and a one. But it gave zombie-like characters killing themselves in front of me.
It was in Geneva. The city had set up water slides in the various parks. It was nice.
My father had to buy a car for my brother and me. An 806 (Peugeot) at 7300 euros precisely. But my brother didn't want it.
I know my dream had something to do with my teeth.

I was on an island, a very strange but very pretty place. There was a tiny old quarter, resembling the old town of Paris. 200m away there was fine sand and the turquoise sea. I believe there was a polytechnic where I worked. I was in charge of organizing a big party. Some of my friends were there as well as my girlfriend to help me in this task. Afterwards, only the details come back to me. I think I was very lucky. Everything I did, I succeeded. There was also a story with a special bird.

I was in an imaginary amphitheater, a very wide but not long room. There were a few students including my girlfriend who looked different than usual. My professor of applied social psychology was giving a course there. He seemed even more complexed, sensitive and paranoid than I actually perceived him to be. We argued over something. Then, it was planned that I teach the second part of the course. The teacher took his place among the students. I was totally unprepared and confessed to this. That's when he got mad and told me to put the microphone down and take my seat. I refused and told him what I thought of him in front of the whole class. I was direct but not mean. The teacher burst into tears, I too had tears in my eyes and I stroked his head. Yet it was not a reconciliation, I still felt contempt for him.

I was in a bar which was also a nightclub, it was quite dark; I was very angry with the bartender because items were going missing, I had lost my coat and shoes; I assaulted the bartender by grabbing his shirt and pulling him towards me.

I was in a square in a city that was supposed to be Paris, but I didn't recognize the place. It seemed more like a small town to me. The sky was gray. I was with a girl who was apparently my girlfriend but she didn't look like my girlfriend at all. We went to a park and there she showed me a tomb; then we left the park and just before the exit door there was a statue of 3 nymphs. This was really liked by my girlfriend for a reason one me ??? she was jealous, but I made it up to her by showing her that I had placed white cows at the exit for her (they were white but there was a blue glow around them).

I was in a street, it was dark and the street was poorly lit (bluish glow). I felt like I was being followed. I turned around and there was indeed a truck following me very closely. When I turned around, the truck fled and it turned into a motorcycle. This motorcycle was driven by my mother. A little further, she went down and her husband also appeared. They were laughing because they wanted to surprise me by coming to visit me from the United States. I was extremely happy and also moved.

I called my ex-girlfriend on the phone to prank her (very vague in the dream). She called me back to tell me that she was very disappointed that I was making fun of her, while I found what I did harmless. Then there was silence on the phone and I just hung up. This scene took place in my childhood room and my current girlfriend was next to me. I was very embarrassed talking to my ex on the phone in front of her. After the call, I justified myself and criticized my ex but my girlfriend said that I saw bad in everything, which made me sad and angry, I was also very ashamed of myself.
