I was in an imaginary amusement park and I was watching a video on a big screen in which the park was made fun of because there were a lot of adults doing the rides and they were having more fun than children. I wanted to check this out and turned to a ride that was built entirely out of wood. There were indeed a lot of adults, but that didn't surprise me. Suddenly, one of the adults, an elderly man with long thin hair, shouted stop as the carousel turned (the carousel consisted of cars placed on oval tracks), he also waved his hands. The merry-go-round then stopped and he got off, he felt very bad. The owner of the carousel, a man in his forties, explained that he placed a fish eye in his carousel because the smell would amplify the emotions felt. Unfortunately, this only worked for children and adults would suffer a great deal of nausea. The owner argued that it was legal and that he had permission from the French government. Moreover, he explained that the placement of such a fish eye mimics the conditions of a 19th century fish market. I felt disgust but also curiosity and anticipation.
I was at the very top of a building, on my roof which was flat. It was sunny. I was fighting against my father and my two sisters, I was very angry and I felt great injustice.

I was in the Uni Mail building of UniGE but the building was slightly different. For example, there were tables for studying in the ground floor. There was also a bluish light in the building. I saw a friend who wanted to sell cards. He ran his finger through the pile of cards and it made a noise that imitated birdsong. It was this noise that captured my attention. I was curious and happy to see him and wanted to buy his cards. He walked oddly, that is to say, he took long walks and the upper part of his body did not move.

I dreamed that I went to the United States with my girlfriend, to Houston. We went there by plane. Then we went from Houston by train to an (imaginary) city called Texas. The journey took 2 minutes. There, I showed my girlfriend a supermarket with products that I particularly liked. I felt joy and pride.
I was fighting against musketeers and when I hit them with my foil, they exploded.

I fight with a girl (Indian or Chinese) during a psychology seminar. Jean (a friend) is there and says that girl always makes drama with everything. Before that, we pass through lots of security rooms to return to the room

In fact we were doing a rally with friends. I don't remember the details but one thing stood out to me. I have a girlfriend who has sun allergies. With her medication she currently has a carrot complexion. It's funny because in my dream she was dressed as a rabbit.

I dreamed that I was celebrating my birthday in a circle on the floor. These friends do not know each other at all, I met them at very different times. Something weird happened. A friend who asked for gloves to eat because she had just been riding.

I dreamed that I was at the dentist. I see myself on the seat with my mouth open as if I were beside myself or that I was the dentist. Afterwards it's blurry but I remember washing my hands right after in the uni toilets this time and flooding the actiwatch I wear for the study.

In fact we were doing a rally with friends. I don't remember the details but one thing stood out to me. I have a girlfriend who has sun allergies. With her medication she currently has a carrot complexion. It's funny because in my dream she was dressed as a rabbit.
Hot night, sex dream
It was weird. There was everything and anything. A guy who works in the same building as me, friends from Marseille
My girlfriend and I were breaking up. Why, I don't know. It was weird because the feelings were weird (like it wasn't us…)
Tody, he was the head of a department of a company and told me what he was doing. OM lost against Grenoble tonight at the Vélodrome. The last game of the season.
I just remember either dreaming about my knee or thinking about it, I don't know.

I felt like I was in my roommate Fred's car and we were driving around Geneva and getting lost all the time. We didn't know where we were going and where we were. By the time I begin to recognize, the alarm clock sounds Too weird the dream, stressful even.

I was in a street that I usually take in Neuchâtel, it was evening, I was alone and I was walking, to go where? I do not know. I also remember that there was an ad for orange cigarettes, then I went to 21 (bar in Neuchâtel) then to the festineuch.

My dream was about the current situation and the France team. It was weird because I couldn't see myself but I still felt like a spectator. Zidane gave advice to the France team to the coach etc. But nothing to do the coach didn't want to hear anything
My mother had pain in her muscles, she couldn't move like she used to. We then thought of multiple sclerosis but she assured me that it was impossible when she had not done any test...

We are, my mother, my sisters and I in our village in France and it is New Year's Eve. Traffic in the center of the village is very bad. We leave the car and decide to go around the village which looks less and less like it and more like a city, on foot. The town (it is no longer a village) is on a slope and all the buildings are Haussmann style or equivalent and in rough stone.
I was dressed in a kimono and was in a dojo with other people. Suddenly a kind of argument broke out between a guy and me and we sort of fought. Then someone separated us.
There were people doing body painting on others for medical reasons.
My two sisters had shaved their heads entirely (Britney Spears style).

This friend and I were on a special train, the kind they only go out for special events, with a cast of (made-up) celebrities in Italy. My friend had actually applied for a position in Italian television and we were waiting for the employer's response.

I had to get to work on time, but everything was getting in my way in every sense of the word. As a result, the stress was mounting more and more and I absolutely couldn't arrive on time for my first day.
I was in the acupuncture clinic (I took this treatment for my pollen allergy) and I wanted a new appointment but in my agenda everything was full, so we couldn't find a date to follow the treatment.

My boss is at my house, in my room and he tells me to tidy up the room more and to modify the constellation of the furniture. He helps me unwittingly I break a completely wooden TV that is his but he doesn't get angry (I break it with something long).

We had soccer practice. What was weird is that we were playing on very, very dry, desert terrain. There was little vegetation and barbed wire. I still remember 2 things, a) once the ball went out of bounds and I had to go get it and go over the barbed wire for it. Around the field it was hilly. I had to go upstairs to pick it up. b) Mato, an older defender (around 30) was there. He made a joke.

I was with my girlfriend and 2 friends in the house of one of the two friends and we talked about the match (Bern-Basel) next Sunday. The two friends had tickets for the match but my girlfriend and I did not (full). The conversation was pleasant and entertaining. Then I was embarrassed because they made fun of my girlfriend and me because we didn't have tickets (just we asked them if they couldn't organize another 2 tickets) and they also made fun of a little bit of her because she is for the Basel club.

I was with a Spanish girl that I know (but not too much) and I didn't know if cheating or not my girlfriend. Finally I kissed her but not much and with a bad conscience. I was in bed with her. I felt a little confused, attracted to her but at the same time afraid that my girlfriend would know. Later, I went out with some friends again I think we had been drinking and we were going through a city (I don't know which one) but I hardly remember that.
I escaped from a prison but I hardly remember. It was with three other people but I don't remember. Then we escaped on a plane. It was a small plane and I put myself more to the right to balance.
I'm on a boat and at one point I'm talking to my classmate. The link and the subject of our conversation escape me.
I am going to see my grandmother in Russia and I am surprised that the prices for train tickets in Russia are displayed in euros.
I meet a friend I haven't seen in 3 years.
I performed for Dr Haus
I was on the plane to Seoul. In Seoul, I saw a lot of snow, which surprised me.
I was going to go out with my classmate (from the old university) and her ex-husband. Our clothes were very naughty while in real life I never had sensual ideas vis-à-vis the couple.

I went to England and found myself in a region of the mountains. It was a weird little village like the ones in horror movies. I remember going up and down in those mountains. Suddenly I found myself in a large ballroom, with music, candles, etc. Among young people in the room, there were many old men dressed in the old fashioned way. My colleague from London explained to me that everyone was waiting for a queen (Black Queen) who rules in this village. When this queen entered the hall, I sensed danger and woke up.
My school friend and I went to the countryside (in fancy cars) to do some work.

This is the story of a 10-12 year old boy whose parents have gone somewhere. The boy who also lived alone in an old rustic house fell under the influence of a neighbor. Also a 10-12 year old boy. The neighbor terrorized the boy and made him maraud. The life of the little one was terrible and he decided to kill his neighbor. But instead of the neighbor he killed a cat (poisoned with dichlorvos which is sold everywhere in Russia).
I listened to an English speech by Barak Obama.
My Arabic-speaking friends taught me a few words in Arabic.
It was a spy story with chases, secret agents, etc. In addition, there was a religious motive, a kind of occultism and magic. The story was very interesting.
I was armed on horseback and fought against other knights. The atmosphere of medieval France. I was injured (physical pain).
I groomed my friends dog. I remember the smell and feel of his hair.

I was at the same conference and I was working on the same subjects as the day before. The people, atmosphere etc. were the same as in reality. After the lecture and the discussion, my teachers told me that the feedback was wrong and that in fact I am a good interpreter.
I was again at this party. We were talking, laughing, singing. Everyone was happy and friendly. A real joy
I witnessed an argument between my mother and my grandmother. They hardly ever argue and I, therefore, felt confused and sad.

I saw an old tower. In the dream I knew it was the life of someone close to me. Then I heard the bell from this tower. It was an important sign but I didn't know how to interpret it. So I was afraid it was a sign that someone was going to die.

In my dreams, I went to Lithuania which looked like the Soviet Union. In Lithuania, I met photomodels with whom I spent the whole day. I don't remember sexual and erotic actions, my dream then was quite puritanical.
I flew and met my father on board (he is an airline pilot).

We sat with my brothers on a pile of grated cheese and we chose music on something that looked like a computer. Then I ate a piece of cheese and went out onto the terrace where one of my brothers was smoking a cigarette.
I was chased by some kind of very powerful villain, I was running around and I felt like I was able to lose him but in the end I found myself surrounded.
A friend was pinching me and hurting me, despite my telling her to stop.

I was in a kind of big banquet with many people I knew. At one point, two friends got into an argument and were rolling on the floor. Me, I saved a slice of Nutella that was in their path and I ate it (= great satisfaction). Then I went to a room with a cartoon and candy.
I dreamed that I received the results of my exams and failed, as well as my friends.

Using a round paintbrush (which I use to paint an old house) I drew a red dot on an unknown wall serving as my target to break this wall using a sledgehammer (also used for this house). I don't know why this wall had to be knocked down.

Tied up in the back of an old American car, between the back seat and the driver's seat, I'm compressed and have trouble breathing. The reason for this kidnapping is unknown to me and the driver has no describable face. Suddenly the car I'm in is visualized from the air revealing its green-cyan (sky blue-green) color on a dusty lane reminiscent of the FAR WEST

On a walk in the evening, I am assaulted by someone male, unshaven, in his fifties but totally unknown. This guy is trying to tame me with words like you're not home at this hour. Quickly mastered, I tell him that if he is in need, it is better to ask than to attack. The scenery turns out to be an ancient stone city, from a time when horse-drawn carriages still circulated on the cobblestones. The bandit is expelled from the city and at the gates of the latter, his entry is watched by photos to compare and guards.

Appearing in an MTV show in which you have to follow an adventurer. It is necessary to repeat a perilous expedition but with the cameras. The dream takes place in a sort of tomb à la Indiana Jones, the light dimmed in order to prepare for the expedition.
I chatted with my friend during the first game. Then I found myself in the countryside with my brother. We saw a murder.
Preparation for the trip to England that I had made during the day.
I felt like I was losing my teeth one by one. I saw my mouth from the perspective of a third party.
I was in a war video game. I was one of the characters and I was fighting so I played actively.
I only remember that I attended a rock concert on a hill in the mountains and there were some rather unusual things going on there, but I don't remember what or with whom I attended the concert.
Evening in a swimming pool.
Trip to Amsterdam and tour of hotels.
A friend and I were walking around town at night when we got mugged. My friend is injured and I am chasing the individual for revenge.
I was having a party at my house with lots of friends and having fun with them.
A party with Greg. There is a music-driven vibe. I flirt with girlfriends, there is general confusion.
I'm at the edge of a swimming pool, I'm teaching my brother to swim.
I am in a field with friends. We're an explorer type with a giant grappling hook.
I go to an Asian restaurant with a female presence. The waiter (who looks like an actor) tells us there's no room until next week.
I travel with my brother in a kind of zeppelin. The space inside is big, it's like a small hotel, I have to go to Italy, I haven't paid for my ticket.
I was taking an exam and I couldn't answer any questions, it's panic.
I'm in a building, but on one side of the building I'm in a French chateau and on the other at home in Sicily. Very nice area there are disputes between my family members

I was on a business trip for some dubious, mafia-type business. I had a dog with me, a German Shepherd. I find myself at a checkpoint, that's where I meet a friend. I then discuss with the customs officer to be able to pass.
We were with several friends in a public place. We discussed things and others, often related to studies. One of the girls felt bad (crying), we supported her.
I had to find the town's firefighters to fill out administrative papers. I wandered around my neighborhood in a bathing suit.
I was stressed about not waking up, or going back to sleep. I was convinced that my alarm clock would not work.

Matthieu (my friend and roommate), was in a 1st year class at Claparède college. We were an authority figure, which made the teacher desperate (I recognized a German teacher I never had, but who had a relatively bad reputation for her stormy and annoying character). At a certain moment, for some reason, Matthieu gave way to great emotion and ended up on my knees, seated and huddled up like a child. We were seated at a table with the girl he is in love with, who is now in London, and a pupil whom I suspect is an imaginative synthesis of twin sisters often together in college. The class was effectively picking up the fundraiser that would go towards one of their projects. I left the class going out into a hallway, tense, with a great pain in my right hand that I no longer controlled. I was anxious about not being able to play the violin properly.

I'm sure I had a dream, and I know my dream had something to do with my violin lesson the night before, but I can't decide if it was pleasant to think about it or not. I don't remember having seen my teacher or having relived my lesson but rather have the feeling of having thought strongly at certain moments of the lesson (in particular the choice of an etude, Kreutzer's II, which I am sure of have heard).

We found ourselves in class for a new year (my group of college friends and myself) there were new faces that I did not recognize and my dream began in French class (our teacher had changed sex, actually a small man, we were in front of a very severe woman, or even director). I was mainly concerned about Fanny who finally decides (in my dream) to meet my expectations and shows me an affection that I have been waiting for for a long time (fantasy realized). The rest of the dream takes place on a study trip. The whole class is ???, Fanny and I are in love, but she remains cold to the idea of ​​social recognition of our relationship. That bothers me. The action probably takes place in the mountains, in a vacation home. Suddenly, my dream evolves and I find myself surrounded by some members of my family who arrived from Colombia in front of a ??? modern (English style). There are a lot of people. Then come tigers that scare away most of my friends. My cousins ​​don't seem intimidated. My dream is??? while I run frightened by the tigers, take refuge in a luxurious hotel where the girl group of my group of friends has already fled. I find no particular meaning in this part of the dream.
I know it was about music and that in the second I found myself playing the violin in front of several people. I was playing well and I was happy.

My third and final dream started at the airport. I took a plane (small which did not reassure me) to go to a country in Eastern Europe whose name I was not sure. I remember waiting for the last moment to board. I took advantage of the waiting room which seemed very familiar, warm. And at the time of going through the door to join the plane, I was prevented. I know that at that moment, I was kissed by a woman that I cannot recognize. The kiss was very simple, very warm and pleasant, almost friendly, without erotic projection. At this moment I remember a sort of mise en abyme of an awakening. I dreamed that I woke up in the room where I slept, very late, at 1:30 p.m. I was beside myself to have missed my alarm clock (for the study and for my violin lesson in the morning) and it was my anger that really made me wake up a few minutes before 8am.

We were my roommates and I thinking about the layout of our apartment space. Some wanted several small enclosed spaces to share and there were two of us who did not understand this choice, my friend Matthieu and myself). The particularity of the scene comes from the fact that we were all subjected to a feeling. Matthew was angry. Sarah was happy, Valentin was sad and I was embarrassed. We talked but I only remember the voices, the words were messy and I remember the thoughts I was having. In general, I dice??? the situation that I considered very immature. This went on for quite a while until I walked down the hall towards the door and we were my roommates and I thinking about the layout of our apartment space. Some wanted several small enclosed spaces to share and there were two of us who did not understand this choice, my friend Matthieu and myself). The particularity of the scene comes from the fact that we were all subjected to a feeling. Matthew was angry. Sarah was happy, Valentin was sad and I was embarrassed. We talked but I only remember the voices, the words were messy and I remember the thoughts I was having. In general, I dice??? the situation that I considered very immature. This went on for quite a while until I walked down the hall towards the door and left the room.  I leave the room.
All night I dreamed of him leaving in many different ways,
My last dream of the night was not to reassure me. I was facing a very dear friend green with anger against me. I was extremely guilty and nothing explains this dream to me.

I think I remember my violin lesson, which I lived shared between spectator and actor. What I hear is that I remember hearing notes coming out of my violin with the impression of being master of it only at times. I also know I discussed it with my teacher but I don't remember what it was about.

Remember in front of my teacher. The memory is very clear this time. I carried my violin with difficulty, it seemed very heavy to me. The sounds that came out were of relatively good quality, my teacher was happy but wanted to see me more relaxed. Several times I saw my brother coming in and out of class, he looked very busy but happy to be. After a while I took the direction of the door and went out into a corridor that of the conservatory.

I found myself surrounded by my class friends, in the room of our French lessons last year. People were relaxed and the teacher absent. I was embarrassed because a friend was angry with me for a girl's story and I often had to talk to him. At one point Matthieu, who had been advising me for a while to calm down, pulled me towards him and led me out of the classroom.

I found myself in a huge student house (with musician friends) having to find my room. I met several people there, mostly friends. Before waking up, I was at the entrance trying to access the central hall by the stairs but they were getting so steep that I fell.
Very unclear, I only remember being in front of a crying friend without knowing what to do. She couldn't speak.

I found myself face to face with my father while eating bread and cheese in his kitchen. We discussed the value of things without understanding each other. The discussion was quite irrational, at least in my memory. It was about my violin. I was oppressed by the idea that he didn't understand me, but the feeling wasn't too unpleasant.
I was at my luthier and had to try some bows. As I played, the bows thickened and turned into a ham and cheese sandwich that I ended up eating.

I found myself facing a class friend who burst into tears without being able to explain why. She was unable to tell me what was happening to her as if the ability to know what was making her sad had been taken away from them. Pained, I could do nothing but wait for my alarm clock.
It was a family discussion (Sunday lunch) and I was upset.

Feeling of being the victim of a set up against demonstrators of the Fête de l'Uni, a sort of rather violent nightmare where I was being beaten up, following the fact that I took someone out of the demonstration.
I had a dream with this Marie, it took place in ski camp. Then afterwards, I had nightmares 2-3 times imagining the scene of poor Marie's crime.

I was therefore during this dream at the beach, at Lake Geneva, with a friend of my group. We supervised a group of young people of about 14 years old, immigrants from the Balkans and on vacation. They were playing and bathing. No particular feelings in this dream, neither satisfaction nor frustration.

I was therefore during this dream at the beach, at Lake Geneva, with a friend of my group. We supervised a group of young people of about 14 years old, immigrants from the Balkans and on vacation. They were playing and bathing. No particular feelings in this dream, neither satisfaction nor frustration.
They broke my watch.

I remember being in Annecy, my home town. We are in the middle of the Cold War and there are American warships at anchor below my house, in the lake…Rather a feeling of protection. Another scene that I remember, reception in a restaurant with the GIs. No exchange souvenirs or anything else. I had to be observant.
I dreamed of being an intern in radiology. Feeling of stress, fear of not being up to it. Feeling of having a lot of work, being overbooked.

I was with my high school friends at a Shell gas station (I remember the logos) and we were filling up our cars talking, there were 3 or 4 of us. One of us was having fun putting diesel instead of gasoline in the other's car and in the end we all put the wrong fuel in our friend's car (it's not funny but we had a lot of fun ...)
My girlfriend's ex was in this dream.
I'm with Véro and Manon we walk in the streets of Geneva without real purpose. We laugh.
I'm going to get my license. The examiner comes over and shakes my hand. He looks like an old biker, ex-junkie. I'm quite confused, we get into the car (...).
My cat lying asleep. Feeling of tenderness towards him. I caress him.
Weird party atmosphere
I'm in the bastions building posed with my friends, and Emre kisses me. (It was horrible and very confusing because I didn't know if it was my boyfriend or not) Horrible impression

We were under a big blanket in the middle of my lawn with my girlfriend and other people I don't know. There was a large mass of large insects above us in the air. There was a loud buzz. We all got ready to lift the blanket and run and we did. We ran to a shed next to my house, then passing under the mass of insects, which followed us, we reached the door of my garage which we closed just behind us.
I see myself waking up in the night, and counting the number of awakenings in the night. At home, in my bed.

A man calls me, worried and in a hurry, he wanted and insisted that I tell him about my troubles. He looked angry. Then he appears towards me. (I can't make out the place, it was outside, not in town). (I don't know this man, neither in my dream nor in reality). He appears before me in disguise. In fact, he had been recomposed, he shows me that his shoulders and head were cut off. There is a woman with him who also appears, her legs have been cut off. When she appears, we're inside a house that I don't recognize. I'm afraid. Then there is movement, I want to run away but I'm paralyzed.

In a classroom (place that I do not recognize). I have to staple sheets together, I'm going a little fast. The teacher tells me there is less risk of making mistakes by putting the stapler in this direction. I am surprised.
I was at Sara's in Mexico.

I was with my parents in France and they had to wait for me to take me to university or to work. I kept talking because I had a lot to tell them. I was preparing my bag and I put lots of things in it. I was going to be late but they said nothing. We were laughing and I only went for a 1/4 hour lesson.
Afterwards I find myself at a meal in a kind of tavern with some friends from France. We had a sundae of ice cream as a starter. We were waiting for I don't know what, so she melted

I am in the mountains in a school class with children. I'm here as an intern. The children go to recess and 3 children stay. We talk a bit and they go on recreation. Time passes and no one returns. So with other people of my age who arrive, we open the classroom and the open bay windows overlook the mountain and the animals. We sit on the desks and play cards while smoking cigarettes and the smoke doesn't bother me. And there, one of my best friends comes in. I jump for joy when I see her and we discuss when we will see each other. Another person with a big schedule to fix the days when we will see each other. After my childhood friend comes home and I cry seeing her so happy to see her. She tells me good I have to go, see you later and she leaves. I'm frustrated because she didn't want to stay with me any longer. After she left, the teacher comes in and tells me that we will start again soon. But we meet outside in the courtyard and a colleague of hers shows me a donkey that she transforms into a rabbit.

I spent my ??? in the forest. We were all lined up on a bench, and the teacher was throwing a rotten plum in front of us to find out the order of appearance, then we all went to a kind of big bunker and the teachers were telling us that we were going to take the oral the inside. There were lots of corridors with lots of dormitories, people sleeping... after I asked a class friend for an element of the course that I didn't understand he explained to me then met and kissed another guy.
I'm trying on pants in a store that I have to exchange because they're too big. And I try a smaller one and it's too small.

I was in a neutral room, a gray cube, and I was having sex with Clothilde, a former classmate (two years ago), at the time I found her rather pretty but very stupid. So curious that I think of her at this time. Exciting but therefore curious dream I don't remember having had any sensations except to feel good.
I just remember being a plumber

I just remember that I arrived at a parking lot by tram 15. A parking lot with cars everything was in a very pale pink tone. And in the parking lot I had an appointment with a person (man I think) that I've never seen for babysitting.

I was at a playground with a fire truck, very slow, neon yellow with a black steering wheel. And then I suddenly had to flee I think because of another baby story. A chase through the city. The one who was chasing me (I don't know him) had the same truck as me. My vision was in normal color. Until in a turn I stop my truck and continue on foot and this time return to the city. As I got out of the truck, I hid behind a bush. My pursuer stops but does not know where I have gone. He takes the wrong path (he is now also on foot). And at this moment I am saved but an almost greater fear sets in, that of being found. So I run. I pass a building and there everything turns yellow (rather flash) and orange. And with each step I change bar or district which are all yellow or range. And from a bar I recognize my pursuer, he hasn't seen me but is coming in my direction. I decide to hide again at (which they are not yellow but white) and my dream stops.

It was winter, on skis, I was going down (usually we go up) on the chairlift and when I got there I lost my pair of gloves (red-black). So I stop and look in the snow. But I found that a glove and not the same color moreover. Until I found a pistachio green pair that didn't match the rest of my jumpsuit at all. And curiously a friend of my brother finds a pair similar to mine hence a certain jealousy.

First of all, arriving in front of the nightclub, we meet a tramp who sniffs the sewers and tells us that we are ugly. Once in the nightclub there was a part outside with a floor where there was 5 cm of water and small ??? where we could dance. Inside it was a normal nightclub.

I was skiing with my brother and my neighbor next to a ski lift where shovels were mounted by hooks on the ski lift. Once the shovels took hold we created jumps on the side of the track. But my dream ends there without having been able to jump these jumps resulting in frustration but the joy of having skied. I heard no noise but normal color.

So we were celebrating the birthday of a friend of my father. It was a surprise. We were preparing everything and my mother's aunt who was helping us was sabotaging everything. She was trying to leave traces behind us. And me, I went behind her to remove what she was doing. For example, we were in a big house and when we entered a wardrobe (???) there were still a lot of secret rooms. So we were in there and this aunt left clothes, papers under the door. She did something else but I don't remember. I just know that it caused me to run away. And during the end of my dream, my cousins ​​were trying to catch me until I woke up.
It was at the gym. My psychology teacher explained to us what to do for a file and he said things that were impossible to do. All the students were angry, but especially me

I dreamed that I was going to the volleyball final at Luc (against I don't remember who) with some girlfriends and that when it was time to leave Roger Federer arrived at my house as if he were part of the family and I woke up
troll war

I was at my cousins ​​and they had huge stocks of markers with refills. We were testing them. Then, I was talking with my aunt's ex-husband about the trip I was going to take with my boyfriend during the summer. He maintained that I had told him that I was going to work there in an auction association when I had never said that and it annoyed me because I had the impression that he was not listening to me not.
I only remember that I was trying to turn around while driving a car but I couldn't because the following cars were following me too closely and too quickly.

I only remember that I had to go to prison with several former comrades because we had been caught up in a spiral and had done a lot of stupid things. This made me sad and frustrated because to enter the prison, we had to go through a library but we were not allowed to borrow books to occupy our time usefully.

I was traveling with my parents and we had to quickly pack our bags and leave because a friend of mine had decided to come and kill us (I don't know why). But we could see that we would never be ready in time. Eventually he arrived but I managed to talk to him, calm him down and convince him not to kill us.
I was driving my mother's car when suddenly I found myself by mistake on a muddy rally track. I felt like I was going to roll over and was destroying the car.
I was at the AC Milan stadium and I played football with the club's players including Paolo Maldini, Gattuso, Kaka and Ambusini. We were playing against a team in blue (probably Inter).

My friend and I had an altercation with three other people, one of whom I knew by sight. I followed a fight in which my friend and I emerged victorious. These events took place in the plain of Plainpalais (Geneva) at the corner of rue Dancet (near the UBS). The tension before and during the altercation rose crescendo. Afterwards for my friend and I, it was much better, probably because we managed to turn the situation to our advantage.

My first dream took place at my workplace. Devices such as the computer, the fax or the telephone did not work or worked very badly. My colleagues were sometimes angry or even frustrated. It was pray for worse.
The second dream echoes my surprise to find my neighbor working in a nightclub, when I had never thought of finding her there. She looked happy to be there.
then, the third dream takes place downtown. There, I meet a friend that I had not seen for a long time. What joy and what satisfaction during my reunion.

I was in a seemingly public place. A weird man was walking around. Suddenly he pulls out a knife for some reason. Another person talks to him and tells him to leave. The suspicious person returns a few minutes later brandishing a knife. The person who had asked him to leave manages to subdue him. I run to lend a hand and control the madman. The police arrive quickly and take the dangerous individual away.

I see an old friend that I had lost sight of. He tells me that he has become a father and shows me his baby. We were very happy to meet again after so many years and different trajectories. The time spent together we talked about the past and our current life.
The dream was about a business meeting. In fact on a briefing between the collaborators (of which I was part) and the person in charge of the organization or the company where I worked.
See you at the bank with a big raffle that I won. A Flip Flip plastic elephant that I will later give to my goddaughter.
CSO competition at Maillys

Childhood friends throw stones at me (??? at war) (anger). I get angry and tell them to stop. They do it and regret what they did. I tell them it's too late and they might have to watch cartoons (punishment).

My dad told me to hurry up (go for it), it's the good job, job, after I told him I met a girl (Liliana). The name of my grandmother (her mother) was Liliane. There is a sense of urgency (no time to waste). Everything takes place in Bern (old town).
I just remember that Catherine Deneuve played the role of my grandmother that we walked in a port where there was a colorful market.

I am somewhere between Friborg and Bern. In some sort of hostel or hotel. My mother asked me to reserve a table in the restaurant for her and a couple of Bernese friends (whom I also know). I omitted his request, and suddenly feel bad and anxious because I fear the reaction of my mother.

My sister-in-law and I have to take the bus. We are in Geneva and it is dark. I do believe it is raining. I forgot to take something with it (I don't know what). I hesitate for a moment and finally decide to go get this thing. I'm feeling time-stressed because I'm going to keep my sister-in-law waiting. My mother will certainly say that once again I forgot something. It seems to me that I pass by a small shopping center where there are spiral staircases. I hurry, I run and I feel the heat rising. I seem to hear the noise of cars, buses, rain and horns. I see fars when I meet my sister-in-law outside at the bus stop. It seems to me that we are near the station. (But I don't see the buildings clearly). I'm relieved to see that my sister-in-law is still here. I feel terrible and sorry for keeping her waiting. I can't tell if she looks angry or not.

I am in the city of Geneva. It's the end of the day (maybe 4 or 5 pm), it's sunny and quite warm. I believe we are in June. I walk around with two suitcases that I have received I don't remember from whom and for what occasion. I find it funny to have received two, because normally I should have received only one. I know I'm happy. It seems to me that I am coming out of work, which I do not know. I am satisfied because I worked. I don't know if it was voluntary work or if I earned money. I feel relieved that the job is done. I walk towards the Coulouvrenière bridge towards the Stand tram stop (direction Plainpalais). I'm curious to know what I received in the suitcase. I stop on the way and open one of the suitcases containing, among other things, three ties. I'm going somewhere. The place looks like the mall where I was before (in the dream with my sister-in-law). I have just come down these spiral stairs when a man tries to take my suitcase which I had opened before. I tell him to let go and leave me alone. He doesn't seem to have understood or listened to me because he's following me. When I find myself in a corner in a kind of room with glass everywhere (like the entrance to a shopping center in an underground car park). It's not me anymore but another young girl. The man becomes threatening and I believe that the girl understood that he wanted to sexually abuse her. The girl, I don't know how, manages to escape and call for help. Not far from there is another man. She goes to him to help and protect her. The man approaches her and enters the glazed room. The young girl, relieved at first, panics when she realizes that the man is blocking the sliding glass door behind him. She is scared that he is an accomplice of the other man. (Here in the dream it's pretty unclear if they abused her or not, who, how and etc... But I'm pretty sure she was sexually assaulted. I feel helpless. I wish so much to be able to do something, to smash the face of these two men. At the same time, I am also relieved that it is no longer me in the dream).

I am on the ski slopes in Graubünden. I have a whole day ahead of me. I go down the first track which is quite flat. There is wind against me. I forgot something above the track, something not essential, but important to me. Even in the dream it is not clear what this thing is. But I think it would reassure me to have it. I still continue to descend the track. It's taking me forever. I'm still worried about that thing I forgot and hesitate to follow up. I'm near the end of the slope when there is a strange man skiing next to me. I do believe he is a madman. He scares me a little. He says something to me as he approaches me. I let him pass me and am finally relieved that he goes even lower down the mountain and disappears. There I stop and decide to turn around. We are already noon I believe. I'm mad at myself because once again I should have done what was on my mind right away. I wasted half my time and I'm going to ruin my skiing day. I go up the slope to reach the top station. When I walk up, I feel very hot. I pass a crowd of people going down and having fun. I finally arrive at the top station. I'm disgusted. My day is ruined and it's because of me. This is where I meet a friend from primary school. We would like to take the gondola to go somewhere else. I don't quite know where. But there are a lot of people and I become more and more anxious at the idea that my day is definitely ruined. It seems to me that the queue was so long that we missed the last gondola.

My dad found it expensive to go to the pool just to do a few lengths. B) there is a bus story. C) I get offered a dodgy job and find out that my dad is doing things that I believe are illegal for his job. The situation becomes threatening for him, he is revealed by the police. d) My mother is very angry with me. We do not talk anymore. I'm very sad and I don't know what to do anymore, confusion. e) My friend from Indonesia is coming to visit me again. But this time it's different. I find her very distant. I'm afraid. I want to cry in her arms because of the differences with my mother. f) There is also a story with dinners and get-togethers with vintage dance buddies.
I am with this friend. Now we are a couple. We are together in Freiburg. We walk together in town, but in the hand and we kiss occasionally. I hold him by the arm at times.
I was elected to the city council and the voters were my friends.
I went shopping to find a dress for my cousin's wedding.
I took a French exam but with strange content and not enough time to do it.
I did a jumping competition with my mare in a place that I did not know.

We were a group on a walk in a country and the footbridge that connected the 2 banks of the river had broken. We had to swim across and not let go of the rope so as not to be swept away by the currents.
I was on vacation.
On vacation with people I didn't know.

At a friend's house there was a burglary in her room. We call the police. The window is broken, there is glass on the floor. Then appears one of the burglars (female), one of the friends who is with us runs after him and catches him. A second burglar comes out with a scalpel a fight breaks out the friend is injured, loses consciousness and comes to himself there is always more or less a fight, group discussion. Waiting for the police, I couldn't wait to hear the siren. I was scared.

Succession of fast scenes with not very logical links. I have already forgotten almost everything. I only remember, buffet of food, director shows me on a game of goose boxes which allow to find missing people or to listen to music. Students form a group (of ...) and take pictures of them...

my ex-boyfriend had decided to beg by choice (refusal of the system) and he asked me to give him an essay on ethics, which was to be 40 pages, for his university course. I had a work on ethics but only 8 pages and I told him that I was no longer in a literary course now (the development of the subject was not going to be appropriate).
I smoked all the time. I was surrounded by children and the smoke was coming at them.

I go to the market with teenagers and buy vegetables. I explain to a young person how to cut them. He asks me what is the hardest part of learning to cook. I answer him that at the beginning, we prepare dishes where we don't really process the food and it's easy. It gets harder when the kitchen becomes abstract.

lots of insects and animals. I lose my godson in an amusement park, I spend hours looking for him without finding him. Her mother is very calm and thinks she is around. I find myself locked in an attraction until the next day. A lady presents me with banknotes (money) from certain countries at certain times, what interests us is certain graphic elements of the banknotes.

There were 4 boys who had to read different types of stories written by them and which spoke about themselves, truthful, invented, awkward lived moment… It was quite difficult for them to expose themselves like that. 4 different boys and each inspired me with a different emotion.

I plan to travel by car (as far as Annecy I believe) on the way I stop at a friend's house and I meet 3 friends there including my boyfriend, but I keep my distance from him and at the same time I'm stressed because I have to go do my laundry
I dreamed that I had the wrong date for my paleo ticket and therefore could not go. I check the dates several times, I call friends, I stress Basically I have to resell my tickets.
I'm in a parking lot, Palexpo I believe. I try to find out how much it will cost me and then I meet lots of stars there, we must talk about music, but I don't remember too much.
The image of the tram that goes to Bernex, I see it advancing on its rails, route de Chancy.
I had to fill out this form, I dream of my dream notebook.
I had to choose a destination for an Erasmus for next year and I was afraid of not being accepted, since they had chosen another candidate. In reality, I'm not going on Erasmus at all.

I had to go on a trip to an English-speaking city whose name I did not remember...I arrive at the bus station and there is a problem with my ticket and I learn at the last minute that I cannot can't leave.

Sea, moon, erotic dream, rollerblades, waves. Travel to an unknown country, rather in the Middle East I believe, with my Syrian friends. Swimming in the sea in the evening with a few people. Walk on rollerblades.

I found myself at the scene of the ancient Cambodian genocide, probably in the Pol Pot execution and detention camps which I remembered from a documentary. I was lying on a bed, it even looks like a cradle. Around me there were 3 or 4 people who scared me. I didn't know what they wanted, but I thought one was an exorcist. But why should I be silent in the face of the Khmer Rouge exorcists on such a beautiful July night? In short, they scared me, they disgusted me and I wanted to leave but I didn't know how. They were all screaming and the more they screamed the more I was scared.

Someone I didn't recognize wanted to put an animal that looked like a turtle in my enclosure where my turtle is. I didn't want to because I knew the beast was going to bite my turtle. And indeed, she bit his left front paw. I wanted to make him drop my turtle so I shot him. and it tore my turtle's leg off. I was afraid. Then the dream started again. The person wanted to put the animal back in my turtle's enclosure. This time, without seeing it, I imagined if the beast grabbed my turtle's head, and it made me anxious.
I was making corrections to my bachelor thesis. Every time I read it, there were lots of mistakes and when I corrected all the document lost its layout. I had to start over each time and time passed.

I was in a huge swimming pool (more like a piece of sea) with buoys to go around). There were huge floating objects. I climbed to the top of a floating tower where I was able to catch a flying ball from above. I was holding it by the string and when I saw that I was going to come out of the secure part, I got scared so I let go of the ball and fell into the water. I ran back to a giant giraffe. With my friend and another person we showed up to the lead. This is where the inflatable giraffe fell.

I remember a little. There were a lot of dream sequences that were almost all things from the day and from my African childhood. I would first like to point out that very often I start thinking about my living condition (because the night is a good advisor) and it is also in this context that I fall asleep and wake up the next day. More often than not, I control my dreams, they are things I desire or repress. This means that I master all the characters, all the places, etc. Tonight, two things seem strange to me in the content of my dreams. The first is a helicopter crash in a nearby concession from my childhood in Cameroon. The device appeared to suppress a demonstration. It passed very low above our heads in the street and crashed a few seconds later in the courtyard of the neighbors of my family compound. All occupants are dead. They were white people I didn't know, all dressed in black jackets. The emergency services brought out their bodies (about five) and I no longer remember what happened (in fact I realize that in this concession there was a series of tragic deaths (the father had died, after his wife and finally their son).

The second dream was about a hike in a mountain that I did not know. I struggled in vain to get to the top. I was younger in this dream and there were other children (girls) playing around me. Suddenly I felt thirsty and crouched down under an oil palm to pick up and crack some palm nuts. It was difficult and I don't remember what happened next. Finally, I found myself in the living room of my in-laws. There were a lot of people that I didn't stare at except one of my friends/boyfriends who didn't inspire me with confidence. He's scammed me several times already. His phone started ringing and the listening was not good. In a series of hello hello, he went out to find the best network and suddenly I wanted to follow his conversation. Suddenly his same brand of phone appeared to me and I put it in his ear. I strangely listen to what the correspondent was saying on the other end of the line and he didn't since he continued to say hello hello. The correspondent kept saying, I'm talking to him and he's not even listening. I kept listening and then she started crying. The problem is that this correspondent was my fiancée. I was very angry and there was a moment of confusion.
I was skiing with the parents of a friend, Céline.
My daddy tells me to gas up the car
My aunt tells me about the money I put in the bank.
I dreamed about the boots I bought on Tuesday night. However, they were neither the same size nor the same shape. They were just the same color.
My dad yelled at me for going out too much.
My ex-boyfriend called me.

I remember a natural disaster. Sea water that keeps rising. I'm with someone I know (I don't know who) and we're looking for a solution so we don't get swallowed up. I see a pontoon and I wonder if it's not a good idea to swim there in order to be high and safe. There are plenty of people around us trying to escape the rising waters. In my dream, there was no building. Only water, walls and people running.

I'm at home in my kitchen and I feel like baking a cake and using the oven. My boyfriend is there too and tells me that we never use the oven because it blows the fuse. My mother arrives from shopping and they ask her if I can use it. She says yes, so we put a log in the oven to get it started. It smokes a lot and the smoke suffocates us. We have to get out of the kitchen.
Still in the kitchen, I remember my sister massaging me while I put the water in the gas stove to heat.

I was in my acting class and I was telling the teacher that I didn't like my role and that the play was too short and not interesting (not funny). The other students agreed with me. So, we had to redo everything, we started from scratch (even though the show was the same evening). So we only did improvisations and it went well. What's weird is that I was in the audience but my other self was playing for me.

I was walking with someone (I forget who) through the fields. There were cows and they ran away when we arrived. The weather was nice and suddenly the cold arrived. Everything had frozen even my friend. My goal in this dream was to save her because in my opinion it was a curse, a trap. Someone wanted to take us to another world.
I'm in my garden with a person I know (I don't remember who). We see a bump in the ground, we try to dig it up and there come out 4 large earthworms and a chicken.

It was around noon and I was going to eat with friends. I took my cat there. I was happy to be in this apartment again. The rest is a blur, I just remember my brother showing up, I left the cat with him, and rushed off with my friend, because we were late for school. We walk quickly in the street, these places are supposed to be familiar to me, but are not (I had the feeling to know them, they were imaginary streets). At one point, we come across a group of people (unknown, but whom we know in the dream) who offer us to sit down with them and smoke cannabis. I refuse, my friend stays. I remember smelling the smell of cannabis.

I am in the lower streets, which are like a medieval market. I meet a Japanese girl (that I know apparently) and I follow her. We find ourselves under a large open tent with a large table and a few people seated that I know (I have the feeling that I know them in my dream, but they do not represent anyone around me). At that moment, a group of people arrives, including children of friends of my parents who are my age and whom I have not seen for years. I'm happy to see them again. They tell me that they learned about my parents' separation and that they are sorry. This remark surprises me, because their separation already dates back a few years and bothers me.

I'm in a car with a friend, Anthony, we arrive in front of Uni Mail. I get impatient with the idea of ​​parking the car and my friend then offers me to get off while he looks for a place. I get out of the car, cross and find a friend, Katia, crossing.

I'm on a bus (TPG) with my friend Eve from college and she's driving the bus. She explains to me that she is still learning. She panics a bit, because she can't stop the bus on the yellow lines, she always brakes too late. I try to reassure her and help her by telling her when to brake. She then tells me that she's stressed because her mother is at the back of the bus watching her, that's why she can't brake at the right time.

I'm with Eve again, but in a completely different place, a house I don't know and this time with a boy who was in class with us, Michaël, and who is in medicine with me this year. Michaël announces to us quite happy that we will be able to dissect the body of a corpse. This is the corpse of Mrs. Slatkine, my biology teacher, when I was twelve years old. I am very excited at the idea of ​​this first practical work but at the same time I am apprehensive. Michaël shows us the corpse and I'm surprised at this coincidence. I smell death and it makes me think we need to change, so we don't get a lot of blood on our clothes. I tell Michaël and Eve and they tell me that it's not necessary, because anyway I'm only going to dissect the toes. Suddenly, I smell blood, which makes me insist. I open the wardrobe in the room and start looking. Michaël and Eve became Fedora and Lou (two sisters). We look together for a moment without finding anything that suits. Fedora says, then, that we have to leave, that we will do the dissection another day. I am reassured and disappointed at the same time. I insist that the body will deteriorate if we wait too long, but we leave.

I'm in a house (a kind of big holiday camp house), with people my age (unknown), medical students. We have sheets that are supposed to be our mock MCQ exams. Others do them. For my part, I do it but only halfway, I walk from room to room and I speak with people, while answering a question from time to time. We only have four hours to complete this exam. After a while I realize that people (in the bedrooms) are starting to get into bed. They tell me that they are finished and tell me that I only have ten minutes left. I remain very relaxed even though I have only done half of the exam and I get down to it.

I'm with Magali and Lou, two friends from the cycle who I still see, as well as with Christian, a boy who was in class with us whom I meet about once a year, but whom I haven't met recently. We are at my house (different place in the dream) and we have to go somewhere, it is evening. I suggest we go there by car. My mother agrees and hands me the keys. I'm surprised that she agrees because I don't have a driver's license yet, although I know how to drive. Also, the car is automatic and I have only driven manual cars. She tells me that it's very simple and explains the differences to which I must pay attention. (Very clear passage, she lists and explains to me the operation of an automatic car in detail. I find myself in the car with Christian, Magali and Lou and I take the car out of the parking space. not reassured by the idea of ​​driving without a license, I leave the wheel to Christian. He drives much too fast. I'm not afraid, but I'm embarrassed because he drives my mother's car recklessly, but I don't dare not criticize his way of driving.
I only remember images of landscape Roman temples from Italy (it's the trees that make me say that) and I know that there were people in my dream.
I run up a hill. I don't run, I run for my pleasure. In any case, I'm with two people, but I don't know if they're people I know or not.
a friend of my brother's in the hallway of my apartment. I remember being surprised that I hadn't recognized him sooner.
In my dream, I was a cashier at Migros. My attendance at work was not very regular. I was therefore afraid of losing my life's work, which made my sleep uncomfortable.
